Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Gulsum Akar, We went to Marmaris with my wife for a holiday. We chose this restaurant as a place for dinner based on the reviews and because we wanted juicy food. When we first went there was a serious queue. You proceed by taking the food you want in the form of an open buffet. Both vegetable dishes and meat dishes were plentiful. There was also dessert for those who wanted it. After you get what you want you pay at the cashier. They don't go through cards they work in cash. There was a lot of food variety. And the food prices were unbelievably cheap. We paid only 84 TL for all the meals here. It included buttermilk and bread. But unfortunately I can't say it's too clean as a place.., dataset/taste/hacinin_yeri_gulsum_akar.png, 5, taste
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Oguzhan Cetin, During my holiday in Marmaris we ate here to fit the food. It's really good that the food is cheap and nice. Eating as much bread as you want is a big plus for those who are not satisfied without bread. It is a place that I can recommend to those who will go to Marmaris. On July 1 there was a small increase but even the price hike is cheap. I leave the photo of the latest prices and breakfast below. there was a serious queue. You proceed by taking the food you want in the form of an open buffet. Both vegetable dishes and meat dishes were plentiful. There was also dessert for those who wanted it. After you get what you want you pay at the cashier. They don't go through cards they work in cash. There was a lot of food variety. And the food prices were unbelievably cheap. We paid only 84 TL for all the meals here. It included buttermilk and bread. But unfortunately I can't say it's too clean as a place.., dataset/menu/hacinin_yeri_oguzhan_cetin.png, 4, menu
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Yasin Kuyu, Prices are very affordable. The menu in the photo cost 108 liras. You have to wait 10-15 minutes for food. Staff is annoying. Well it tastes good. Boiled meat was delicious., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/hacinin_yeri_yasin_kuyu.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Orhan Kapu, Turkey's cheapest artisan restaurant and its food is delicious!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hacinin_yeri_orhan_kapu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Ozgur Sati, I don't know what you will look for in terms of price performance point; taste; but yigit restaurant writes a big plus for those who come to work in this region., dataset/menu/hacinin_yeri_ozgur_sati.png, 3, menu
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Arda Karaca, Generally good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hacinin_yeri_arda_karaca.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, İrem Eren, What you see is 125 TL in total. It's a pretty convenient place. We can say that it is an artisan restaurant; you should not expect a restaurant; but they are still quite good in terms of price and performance. As of July 1; prices will increase, dataset/taste/hacinin_yeri_irem_eren.png, 5, taste
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Nadia Salim, Delicious food at rock bottom prices. Friendly staff; Highly recommend, dataset/taste/hacinin_yeri_nadia_salim.png, 5, taste
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Mehmet Eser, Every time I go, I still experience the amazement I experienced years ago as if it were the first time. There is no need to explain. Folk hero is a business., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/hacinin_yeri_mehmet_eser.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Celal Ozer, The most f/p of all businesses I've seen., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hacinin_yeri_celal_ozer.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Haci'nin Yeri - Yigit Lokantasi, Onur Celebi, The food was just like the ones my mother made. Prices were reasonable., dataset/taste/hacinin_yeri_onur_celebi.png, 5, taste
Pizza Fellas, Kadir Tasci, The ambiance of the place is nice; when we went; there was a lot of queue; and after waiting for a while; they took our place. The friend who took our order said half a half pizza and we preferred half chicken and half steak. Two people were easily satisfied; a lot of patterns., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pizza_fellas_kadir_tasci.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Pizza Fellas, Serkan Colak, Flavor : It has nothing but dough taste. Labor : Not befitting a touristic place. Service : There was no wet wipes and napkins on the table, but there was no sympathetic family to say. This service and this taste were not available at this price., dataset/taste/pizza_fellas_serkan_colak.png, 2, taste
Pizza Fellas, Selim Cun, It is in the center; easy to reach; close to the parking lot; the prices are partially affordable; the products are delicious but not quite satisfying; the seating places are cramped; the place is a little flat., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pizza_fellas_selim_cun.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Pizza Fellas, Zeki Celik, They make delicious pizza with nice ingredients on thin dough. Slice pizza and all pizza options are available. You can try two different flavors as a whole by making two different choices for the whole pizza. We wanted the mushroom and sausage. It was very nice; warm; and it was cooked in its consistency without drying the ingredients., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pizza_fellas_zeki_celik.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Pizza Fellas, Mustafa Caliskan, It's in a nice place but it's very small and their pizza is not that good to be exaggerated. Pizza dough is nice and thin. They do not offer advice to the customer., dataset/taste/pizza_fellas_mustafa_caliskan.png, 3, taste
Pizza Fellas, Deniz Bilgin, I strongly recommend. If I come to the taste part; it was very enjoyable to eat with their special sauces. Also the whole pizza was huge., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pizza_fellas_deniz_bilgin.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Pizza Fellas, Cihan Tas, It is very tasty; similar to Italian pizzas. Roast beef and mohair 180 TL; other pizzas 150 TL. An adult male eats 6 slices; pizzas are one size and 8 slices., dataset/menu/pizza_fellas_cihan_tas.png, 4, menu
Pizza Fellas, Seda Sinem, Do not come around Marmaris and do not leave without eating pizza at Pizza Fellas. We ate mixed pizza; they can make two types of pizza. So delicious!, dataset/taste/pizza_fellas_seda_sinem.png, 5, taste
Pizza Fellas, Nesrin Kuyumcu, I never thought that the best pizza I've ever eaten would be in Akyaka. Thin pizzas are very tasty and the options are very good. We recommend it to everyone who comes to Akyaka., dataset/menu/pizza_fellas_nesrin_kuyumcu.png, 5, menu
Pizza Fellas, Okan Uslu, It was as if a very delicious Italian chef had come out of his hands. You can eat with pleasure. The owners are very good people. I recommend., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pizza_fellas_okan_uslu.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Pizza Fellas, Huseyin Uysal, The pizza is big enough for 2 people. The dough is very thin. Price is between 120-140 TL., dataset/taste/pizza_fellas_huseyin_uysal.png, 4, taste
Cafe Inn, Dila Kocatepe, The environment; the interest and friendliness of the employees; the taste is incredible. It is so beautiful inside that you do not prefer to sit at the bottom of the sea. Depending on the day; there are also things that are not written on the menu; be sure to check it out. Hours have passed since the meal; we are still talking about the beef brisket., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_dila_kocatepe.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Cafe Inn, Hooman Sadati, Without any taste how they are at the first rank!!!! We ate cafe Inn pizza. It was 70 tl., dataset/taste/cafe_inn_hooman_sadati.png, 1, taste
Cafe Inn, Serap Gunay, Pizza is delicious.. I can say it is one of the rare tastes. Prices are in the 200-300 range and one pizza is more than enough for two people if you are not very hungry. The scenery is already gorgeous., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_serap_gunay.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Cafe Inn, Tugba Gunaydin, The vegan breakfast made me extremely happy. It was nice., dataset/menu/cafe_inn_tugba_gunaydin.png, 4, menu
Cafe Inn, Can Ozdemir, Whatever we ate was good. The Italian Restaurant is the first thing that comes to mind; apart from pizza and pasta; ciger yahni was successful; purslane salad; presentations are successful. Taste point in Datca., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_can_ozdemir.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Cafe Inn, Berk Basarir, Very enjoyable beautiful place. Pizza salad food taste is great., dataset/taste/cafe_inn_berk_basarir.png, 5, taste
Cafe Inn, Mert Ozer, Its breakfast is more satisfying than the places around it., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_mert_ozer.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Cafe Inn, Kain Dijkman, Nice intimate restaurant. Good service. Eye for detail. Clean. Really good food; well presented., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_kain_dijkman.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Cafe Inn, Sarp Kendirci, The food is delicious but a little pricey. The best Cappucino in Datça is here.., dataset/menu/cafe_inn_sarp_kendirci.png, 3, menu
Cafe Inn, Zafer Togay, It's a very delicious; beautiful small business; but the appointment is a bit difficult to find; the pizzas are great Cafe Inn pizza and a wonderful 4 cheese and brownie as dessert. Thank you for your good wishes., dataset/taste/cafe_inn_zafer_togay.png, 5, taste
Cafe Inn, Eren Kesti, When I went; I waited for almost 20 minutes for the waiters to take care of me. The taste was not bad. The surrounding was beautiful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cafe_inn_eren_kesti.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Olgayali Yilmaz, It is a very, very expensive place. It took 30 minutes for 2 drinks to arrive., dataset/menu/riviera_olgayali_yilmaz.png, 3, menu
Riviera, Gorkey Bardakci, I had the creamy chicken vegetable stew. It tasted excellent. It was quite satisfying. The environment is beautiful and spacious., dataset/taste/riviera_gorkey_bardakci.png, 5, taste
Riviera, Mehmet Yaliniz, quality service and rich menu. the attitude of the staff is really excellent. A business that deserves 5 stars., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/riviera_mehmet_yaliniz.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Goksel Aybek, The sushi was too small so it was not possible to taste the ingredients; the rice was overcooked and lacked flavor; it was missing except for the tail of the shrimp., dataset/taste/riviera_goksel_aybek.png, 2, taste
Riviera, Cahide Koral, The staff was very engaged. Service and taste were perfect., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/riviera_cahide_koral.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Aya Zhol, Perfect location next to the sea. Music; light in the evening lounge atmosphere. In short; everything is beautiful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/riviera_aya_zhol.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Metin Tumay, It was very expensive, but taste wasn't bad., dataset/menu/riviera_metin_tumay.png, 2, menu
Riviera, Yılmaz Unal, Good quality service; nice customer service; they are happy to help with a smile., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/riviera_yılmaz_unal.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Alex Aali, Scrambled eggs with casserole and toast waited 30 minutes. At 12:30pm the main menu was denied and showed only breakfast available. Prices are much higher than other places., dataset/taste/riviera_alex_aali.png, 2, taste
Riviera, Yahya Nawar, Nice view, good staff, clean place and nice atmosphere., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/riviera_yahya_nawar.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Riviera, Nirmal Narayan, Nice food and good service; located just near the beach as well., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/riviera_nirmal_narayan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Gamze Aciogli, It was very nice to be greeted with a smile when we first entered; we went with my wife; the services are very fast; the empty services are removed

Prices are much higher than other places., dataset/taste/riviera_alex_aali.png, 2, taste

Riviera, Nirmal Narayan, Nice food and good service; located just near the beach as well., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/riviera_nirmal_narayan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Gamze Aciogli, It was very nice to be greeted with a smile when we first entered; we went with my wife; the services are very fast; the empty services are removed immediately; the washbasins were hygienic and clean; and I would recommend a very reasonable place., dataset/taste/sakip_usta_gaziantep_gamze_aciogli.png, 4, taste
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Murat Erdemir, Kebabs are good; trotters are good; desserts are good. Actually; the decor part of the atmosphere is good. Only a lot of noise comes from the kitchen part. Employees are smiling., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sakip_usta_gaziantep_murat_erdemir.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Berat Türk, If you come to Antep; sit down and taste the Beyran soup; served plain and with garlic., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sakip_usta_gaziantep_berat_turk.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Agah Beyoglu, I asked for garlic; but I had a hard time getting the taste of the meat from the garlic flavor. I'll try again with little or no garlic. Quite satisfying. I like the taste too; you should definitely try it., dataset/taste/sakip_usta_gaziantep_agah_beyoglu.png, 4, taste
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Serap Keskin, Taste was amazing! Price was not high., dataset/menu/sakip_usta_gaziantep_serap_keskin.png, 4, menu
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Ahmet Coban, When I ate it in the past; it tasted very good; I think the chef has changed. The atmosphere was average., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sakip_usta_gaziantep_ahmet_coban.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Huseyin Bulut, We were very satisfied. I strongly recommend trying it. Delicious appetizers come with the meals., dataset/taste/sakip_usta_gaziantep_huseyin_bulut.png, 5, taste
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Merve Balci, The food tastes good. The atmosphere of the place was not very attractive., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sakip_usta_gaziantep_merve_balci.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Goktug Yigit, We ate 1 mumbar and 1 kusleme and paid 310 TL. The meals were very tasty., dataset/taste/sakip_usta_goktug_yigit.png, 4, taste
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Kutay Demir, Very cheap and delicious!, dataset/menu/sakip_usta_gaziantep_kutay_demir.png, 5, menu
Sakip Usta Gaziantep, Ali Kaya, Ayran came when the meal was over; the food was very bitter., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sakip_usta_gaziantep_ali_kaya.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Mustafa Ay, Although the prices are a little high; the quality is high so it does not disappoint. The taste was very good; well done!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_mustafa_ay.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Yalcin Cokzehir, We ordered Etli Ali Nazik Kebab. They said he was the most famous. We ate meat with yogurt. The food was cold., dataset/taste/imam_cagdas_yalcin_cohzehir.png, 2, taste
Imam Cagdas, Yusuf Gur, We came because it is a very famous place. They had really delicious food., dataset/menu/imam_cagdas_yusuf_gur.png, 4, menu
Imam Cagdas, Humeyra Akyuz, Ali nazik was 240 tl lahmacun 50 tl even tea with a fee of 5 tl. We visited so many places; this was the most expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_humeyra_akyuz.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Muhammet Ikbal, The taste was very good but the prices were also very high., dataset/taste/imam_cagdas_muhammet_ikbal.png, 5, taste
Imam Cagdas, Olcay Akin, Located in Gaziantep historical bazaar; the place stands out with its beautiful and spacious ambiance. I liked the place very much; we came for dessert after dinner., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_olay_akin.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Duygu Er, I had the chance to taste many flavors; all of them were very good; I was amazed by Ali Nazik Kebab., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_duygu_er.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Ceylan Birgun, The restaurant that made our four-day Gaziantep holiday poison! There is already excessive noise; it is impossible to hear the person next to you. The waiters are indifferent; the order takes too long to arrive., dataset/menu/imam_cagdas_ceylan_birgun.png, 1, menu
Imam Cagdas, Hakan Unveren, They sold us rotten pistachios, it sucks!, dataset/taste/imam_cagdas_hakan_unveren.png, 1, taste
Imam Cagdas, Hakan Solak, I don't know why we ate here despite the exorbitant prices. A portion of kebab or sis meat product starts from 220 TL as of the end of June 2023. Naturally; you expect a good portion; but a tiny portion in the middle of the plate., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_hakan_solak.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Imam Cagdas, Sinan Ozen, A great business that does not compromise on its taste; lahmacun, garlic kebab; yoghurt kebab; the smile of the waiters; everything is in place; thank you very much for the nice service and delicious food., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/imam_cagdas_sinan_ozen.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, Tarik Yuce, The breakfast was very good; I recommend it; the presentations were also eye-catching. We paid 240tl for the table you see in the photo; including 6 teas and 2 Turkish coffees., dataset/taste/gold_semaver_tarik_yuce.png, 5, taste
Gold Semaver, Yasemin Uzuner, The place is beautiful. The staff was very nice. We asked for tiramisu. It was very fresh and beautiful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/gold_semaver_yasemin_uzun.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, Gokhan Efe, Beautiful place. The breakfast is said to be good. I had tea in the evening; it was delicious. It tastes like a samovar. The environment is calm. The music is jazz style; suitable for the calm and soft atmosphere., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gold_semaver_gokhan_efe.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, Bunyamin Engin, Hookah and ambiance is super!, dataset/menu/gold_semaver_bunyamin_engin.png, 5, menu
Gold Semaver, Mehmet Mercan, They have a problem with the service; but if you're going to drink tea; they do it well. Your tea is always hot over the fire., dataset/taste/gold_semaver_mehmet_mercan.png, 3, taste
Gold Semaver, Hakan Tekelioglu, Some of the coffee I wanted came spilled; the coffee tasted dry. Also; my wife's order was wrong., dataset/taste/gold_semaver_hakan_tekelioglu.png, 1, taste
Gold Semaver, Mehrin Kuru, Great., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/gold_semaver_mehrin_guru.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, Geordon Omand, Lovely; affordable seafront spot to while away the afternoon smoking nargile and playing backgammon (tavla). Super hospitable employees and enjoyable ambience., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gold_semaver_geordon_omand.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, ALi Bes, A cheap and delicious place. If you are passing by; you should not continue without having a cup of tea., dataset/taste/gold_semaver_ali_bes.png, 4, taste
Gold Semaver, Bayram Kale, Seaside great view!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/gold_semaver_bayram_kale.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Gold Semaver, Beril Kendirci, Prices are nice, dataset/menu/gold_semaver_beril_kendirci.png, 4, menu
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Yeliz Eker, Bitter; mango; Bodrum tangerine; honey almond; Big Babas; mastic gum; walnut; blackberry and forest fruit definitely recommend.., dataset/taste/fethiye_dondurmacisi_yeliz_eker.png, 5, taste
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Murat Yesilci, The prices are cheap from the center; the ice cream is legendary; don't miss out; it's worth waiting in line; it's the best ice cream shop in Fethiye. Real milk ice cream, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_murat_yesilci.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Arch Ao, Absolutely perfect come try it.., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_arch_ao.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Zloy Grazhdanin, Terrible. This is a lie. This is not ice cream! This gum is an ice cream substitute., dataset/taste/fethiye_dondurmacisi_zloy_grazhdanin.png, 1, taste
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Aygun Nurca, As I was crossing the road; I noticed that we stopped. The light ad is very good because everything has ice cream icons. The only normal price I've seen in Fethiye is 6 TL., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_aygun_nurca.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Bekir Tunca, The atmosphere of the place was nice; if you want to taste the ice creams; I can say that it is an ordinary ice cream that you can eat anywhere., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_bekir_tunca.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Batuhan Kinik, It literally gave me the feeling of chewing sugar. It's not even about ice cream., dataset/taste/fethiye_dondurmacisi_batuhan_kinik.png, 2, taste
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Semanur Cetin, We visited with my friends. The lemon one was great!, dataset/taste/fethiye_dondurmacisi_semanur_cetin.png, 4, taste
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Derya Halis, A great taste. I went on recommendation; it was really true. I also recommend it to you., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_derya_halis.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Burak Aydogdu, Their prices are very reasonable and their ice creams are delicious. There is not only ice cream but also dessert sales inside. There are many options for ice cream; which is a very nice detail., dataset/taste/fethiye_dondurmacisi_burak_aydogdu.png, 5, taste
Fethiye Dondurmacisi, Ahmet Oz, On the way to the city center of Fethiye; a sweet place caught our attention. The ice cream cone-shaped totem on the road was very original., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fethiye_dondurmacisi_ahmet_oz.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Ilknur Guntepe, The hamburger bread was very nice. I didn't like his meatballs very much.Orders are coming out very quickly; and the working friends are very kind; thank you., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_ilknur_guntepe.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Fethi Duhan Calik, A place that makes unorthodox burgers in Samsun. The hamburger bread is big and wide with lots of sesame seeds., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_fethi_duhan_calik.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Gun Oksay, It's a very nice place; the hamburger is very nice. The staff is very good; there is a children's playground, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_gun_oksay.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Hatice Isik, The place is nice; the waiters work sulkily. The location; service and presentation are beautiful. And his hamburger might be the most mediocre hamburger I've ever had. There is no meat

A place that makes unorthodox burgers in Samsun. The hamburger bread is big and wide with lots of sesame seeds., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_fethi_duhan_calik.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Gun Oksay, It's a very nice place; the hamburger is very nice. The staff is very good; there is a children's playground, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_gun_oksay.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Hatice Isik, The place is nice; the waiters work sulkily. The location; service and presentation are beautiful. And his hamburger might be the most mediocre hamburger I've ever had. There is no meat taste in the meatball., dataset/taste/my_friends_burger_hatice_isik.png, 2, taste
My Friends Burger, Olcay Albayrak, Mushroom burger the meat stays thin inside the huge burger bread; and the meat and mushrooms do not stay in the bread because of the sauce applied on the bread., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_olcay_albayrak.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Mahzun Zara, They have really saturated menus. The prices are very good; and as a place with a very nice interior and exterior decor with sea views; I would definitely recommend it at the same time., dataset/menu/my_friends_burger_mahzun_zara.png, 5, menu
My Friends Burger, Gonul Bilir, I never liked the service very bad; when we brought the wrong burger and returned it; we had to wait that much longer. The potatoes were terrible; the only onion rings and mushrooms were beautiful. I will never go to this place again., dataset/taste/my_friends_burger_gonul_bilir.png, 1, taste
My Friends Burger, Yunus Ercin, The burger is successful; but the service is very slow; I came to the place 2 times; they bring the order incorrectly., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/my_friends_burger_yunus_ercin.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
My Friends Burger, Nilufer Yilmaz, The menu content is beautifully varied and satisfying., dataset/taste/my_friends_burger_nilufer_yilmaz.png, 5, taste
My Friends Burger, Firat Ismail, The price was not right; I bought a 2-piece menu; the burger and bread did not taste good., dataset/taste/my_friends_burger_firat_ismail.png, 2, taste
My Friends Burger, Ayhan Aydin, The prices were generally reasonable; the tastes were also good enough., dataset/menu/my_friends_burger_ayhan_aydin.png, 4, menu
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Fatih Altinkaya, The menus offered by the friendly staff are something else; the flavors we have tasted., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mcdonalds_fethiye_fatih_altinkaya.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Suleyman Keskin, I would like to thank the service in Fethiye branch and especially Mr. Samet; the official here, for his interest and relevance., dataset/taste/mcdonalds_fethiye_suleyman_keskin.png, 4, taste
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Di Nessa, The menu is incomplete; not much; usually a disaster with happy sweet toys; felt-tip pens and a few cardboard coloring pages., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mcdonalds_fethiye_di_nessa.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Ahmet Gedici, Taste is exactly the same as in classic hamburgers; prices are extra high., dataset/menu/mcdonalds_fethiye_ahmet_gedici.png, 4, menu
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Metmet Sahin, Every time I come to Fethiye; I stop by and fill my stomach with pleasure., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mcdonalds_fethiye_mehmet_sahin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Cagla Cemre, In general; everything was good; but the tables were not collected during the 35-45 minutes I was there. It was messy inside., dataset/taste/mcdonalds_fethiye_cagla_cemre.png, 4, taste
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Salih Ural, The ambiance of the place looks a bit old., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mcdonalds_fethiye_salih_ural.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Hatice Akin, They are very fast and the food tastes good too., dataset/taste/mcdonalds_fethiye_hatice_akin.png, 5, taste
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Serafettin Ozturk, The potatoes were almost dead and tasteless., dataset/taste/mcdonalds_fethiye_serafettin_ozturk.png, 2, taste
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Kivanc Kulaksizoglu, I didn't like the gloomy; dark atmosphere of the environment; the toilets are dirty; you are disgusted to wash your hands., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mcdonalds_fethiye_kivanc_kulaksizoglu.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Mcdonalds Fethiye, Serdar Yıldız, There was a hair in the fries; disgusting., dataset/menu/mcdonalds_fethiye_serdar_yildiz.png, 1, menu
Pukka Marmaris, Brad Murphy, In terms of price; it is above Marmaris prices. In other words; there are menus with prices above the average. I was satisfied with almost everything I ate and drank., dataset/taste/pukka_marmaris_brad_murphy.png, 4, taste
Pukka Marmaris, Gursel Vatansever, It is a place where the food is as amazing as the cocktails. The sole fish was very good. employees are very engaged., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pukka_marmaris_gursel_vatansever.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Pukka Marmaris, Ozgur Kaya, Slagethi all nero was excellent. Beef ribs were always tender enough. Cheek, on the other hand; has preserved its taste even though its collection is a little small. If deterioration was to come; the services were passed and the environment was much expected., dataset/menu/pukka_marmaris_ozgur_kaya.png, 3, menu
Pukka Marmaris, Can Oz, As we were passing on the road; it was pleasing to our eyes and we dived in. It was good overall., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pukka_marmaris_can_oz.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Pukka Marmaris, Bekir Unsal, For people living in Marmaris; it is a beautiful place to visit in summer and winter. I recommend you to try liver because they serve it in a way I have never tried before and because of its amazing taste., dataset/taste/pukka_marmaris_bekir_unsal.png, 5, taste
Pukka Marmaris, Huseyin Koca, Wonderful place where you can go with your family and have fun; nice place with live music..., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pukka_marmaris_huseyin_koca.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Pukka Marmaris, Taner Gun, Prices were slightly higher than peers., dataset/menu/pukka_marmaris_taner_gun.png, 4, menu
Pukka Marmaris, Deniz Tekin, Pukka is a restaurant by the sea where you will have the most beautiful pictures and videos where you can organize a nice organization in Marmaris., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pukka_marmaris_deniz_tekin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Pukka Marmaris, Adem Can, Great concept and very tasty food., dataset/taste/pukka_marmaris_adem_can.png, 5, taste
Pukka Marmaris, Selcuk Uras, Popular place for Winter and Summer; food and drink menu wide enough and delicious., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pukka_marmaris_selcuk_uras.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Pukka Marmaris, Dogukan Mert, Delicious. However; prices are as high as Marmaris in general in 2021., dataset/menu/pukka_marmaris_dogukan_mert.png, 4, menu
Starbucks Bodrum, Taner Bayburtlu, The interior design is simple and pleasant; with balconies and upper floors with sea views., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_taner_bayburtlu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Tugba Bal, I can say that my worst flat white experience. "Would you like milk?" they said. I drank more milk than coffee., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_tugba_bal.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Ahmet Gelegen, A great starbucks branch located in Bodrum center / bazaar / port. It's great because the layout; the environment; the place and the service are very successful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_ahmet_gelegen.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Sule Kivrak, The place is very narrow; I can say it's the worst starbucks I've ever seen., dataset/taste/starbucks_bodrum_sule_kivrak.png, 2, taste
Starbucks Bodrum, Alparslan Alatur, It was a pleasant snack; a refreshing drink in hot weather., dataset/taste/starbucks_bodrum_alparslan_alatur.png, 5, taste
Starbucks Bodrum, Tugrul Gul, The view is super, the cleanliness is bad, the location is very good, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_tugrul_gul.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Omer Kavak, The place is so sweet. but it gets too crowded in the evenings., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_omer_kavak.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Arif Kar, Familiar coffee that I taste, dataset/menu/starbucks_bodrum_arif_kar.png, 3, menu
Starbucks Bodrum, Beril Yilmaz, Had to stop by for a take out coffee during the morning hours., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_beril_yilmaz.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Mustafa Parlak, Employees are very warm. in a very pleasant location., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/starbucks_bodrum_mustafa_parlak.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Starbucks Bodrum, Yasemin Catalkaya, The employees are very good and caring. Best Starbucks.., dataset/taste/starbucks_bodrum_yasemin_catalkaya.png, 4, taste
Churchill Bistro, Sena Sarioglu, Here you can find by far the best 4-cheese pizza you can eat in Bodrum. On top of that; you may have reasons to come back again and again with the unusual taste and presentation of the magnolia., dataset/taste/churchill_bistro_sena_sarioglu.png, 5, taste
Churchill Bistro, Elif Bengu, A place we found by chance during the winter season. First of all; we sat down to drink coffee and the environment was so spacious and calm that I was able to hold a meeting that I had to do over the web without any problems., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/churchill_bistro_elif_bengu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Churchill Bistro, Erkan Aka, I have never seen a pizza with such a thin pizza dough that the material did not fall apart. Pizza mista is a great choice for mixed lovers., dataset/menu/churchill_bistro_erkan_aka.png, 4, menu
Churchill Bistro, Baris Demirci, It is a very nice place to watch the matches; when it is closed in winter., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/churchill_bistro_baris_demirci.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Churchill Bistro, Sibel Sarihan, A pleasant place with a beach; delicious food, dataset/taste/churchill_bistro_sibel_sarihan.png, 5, taste
Churchill Bistro, Rumeysa Oncel, It is a place where you can both enter at home and spend time with pleasure and eat and drink. The beach is very beautiful; your sea is clean. The food is also very good., dataset/menu/churchill_bistro_rumeysa_oncel.png, 5, menu
Churchill Bistro, Bora Ozkut, It is a business that serves 2 orange juices that are not on the breakfast menu and that I did not order; as if they were on the menu; and charges an extra 40 TL., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/churchill_bistro_bora_ozkut.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Churchill Bistro, Bojan Kuruc, We sat at the table; 10m away from the water; went for a swim and then came back to our table. They have changing cabins inside; very clean. Tried some cocktails and they were really good; but prices are like in Kos; Greece where we came from., dataset/taste/churchill_bistro_bojan_kuruc.png, 5, taste
Churchill Bistro, David Kaeser, It is a restaurant-bar with an extraordinary ambiance. It has an excellent location on Bodrum Beach. The service is top notch and leaves nothing to be desired., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/churchill_bistro_david_kaeser.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Churchill Bistro, Ali Suca, Seaside; pleasant place; mediocre food; owners concerned., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/churchill_bistro_ali_suca.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Churchill Bistro, Michael Streich, Beautifully located restaurant on the beach; very nice staff and very good value

Leman Kultur, Merve Gun, Nice place with a view. Not bad in terms of food but ordinary., dataset/taste/leman_kultur_merve_gun.png, 3, taste

Leman Kultur, Alper Ates, It has a location by the sea; a layout that allows for indoor and outdoor seating. Their waiters are nervous and sometimes indifferent., dataset/menu/leman_kultur_alper_ates.png, 3, menu
Leman Kultur, Yilmaz Yilmaz, It was very nice that the food was delicious; the place was facing the beauty of Alanya Castle and especially all the staff were interested., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/leman_kultur_yilmaz_yilmaz.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Leman Kultur, Emine Korkmaz, Good salep was good; the employees were smiling.., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/leman_kultur_emine_korkmaz.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Leman Kultur, Mesut Dursun, Food was tasteless. The waiters were not smiling at all., dataset/taste/leman_kultur_mesut_dursun.png, 3, taste
Leman Kultur, Mehmet Sahin, We wanted mint lemonade; they put mint syrup in the lemonade; when we asked; they said that's what we do; but if you don't like it; we'll change it and they changed it., dataset/menu/leman_kultur_mehmet_sahin.png, 2, menu
Leman Kultur, Ozer Celik, A large spacious place. If you want; you can relax inside and have something to drink., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/leman_kultur_ozer_celik.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Leman Kultur, Melis Demir, Location is nice. We love it as a family. Pizza was delicious., dataset/taste/leman_kultur_melis_demir.png, 5, taste
Leman Kultur, Ufuk Canatan, Stylish; decent and clean place. I advise., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/leman_kultur_ufuk_canatan.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Leman Kultur, Serhat Sutcu, In a beautiful location by the sea; sometimes it gets very crowded; the service can be delayed, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/leman_kultur_serhat_sutcu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Tatbak, Nisa Akdeniz, I think it came with a change in taste with the price update., dataset/menu/tatbak_nisa_akdeniz.png, 2, menu
Tatbak, Nafican Tatlici, It's nice; but it's very late. I place an order; it arrives an hour later; I would be happy if it was a little faster., dataset/taste/tatbak_nafican_tatlici.png, 3, taste
Tatbak, Mehmet Erbagci, A delicious doner., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tatbak_mehmet_erbagci.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Tatbak, Suleyman Konus, the ambiance was nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tatbak_suleyman_konus.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Tatbak, Ahmet Takir, Interest was good; but doner was a complete disaster. First of all; it came cold; there was no proper sauce in it; there was so much onion that I could not taste the meat at all., dataset/menu/tatbak_ahmet_takir.png, 2, menu
Tatbak, Mert Cakir, Awesomeee, dataset/taste/tatbak_mert_cakir.png, 5, taste
Tatbak, Gokay Baydemir, Delicious doner. I went there with my friend, that was she's first. She liked too., dataset/taste/tatbak_gokay_baydemir.png, 5, taste
Tatbak, Unsal Ceylan, Nice place, good price; good quality, dataset/menu/tatbak_unsal_ceylan.png, 5, menu
Tatbak, Leyla Ciftci, Delicious!, dataset/taste/tatbak_leyla_ciftci.png, 4, taste
Tatbak, Baran İsci, It was one of the best doner I've ever eaten in my life. Thank you very much., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tatbak_baran_isci.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Tatbak, İsil Colak, There were problems with cleaning. Chefs must wear gloves., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tatbak_isil_colak.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Mehmet Oz, The atmosphere is very nice; the flavors are also very good; but the prices are a bit high., dataset/taste/guzel_koy_cafe_mehmet_oz.png, 4, taste
Guzel Koy Cafe, Mustafa Coskun, We went for breakfast in the morning; the atmosphere is nice. breakfast items were good and tasty., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/guzel_koy_cafe_mustafa_coskun.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Havva Temiz, The cafe was cheap enough; I ate with my family., dataset/menu/guzel_koy_cafe_havva_temiz.png, 5, menu
Guzel Koy Cafe, Ceyda Cicek, We ordered breakfast; the table was full. It was truly fascinating. I advise., dataset/taste/guzel_koy_cafe_ceyda_cicek.png, 5, taste
Guzel Koy Cafe, Derin Goktug, The indoor atmosphere was nice; but I can't say the same for the outdoor, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/guzel_koy_cafe_derin_goktug.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Teslime Toptas, We were very satisfied from the staff to the meal., dataset/taste/guzel_koy_cafe_teslime_toptas.png, 5, taste
Guzel Koy Cafe, Yigit Oztunc, Ambiance was good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/guzel_koy_cafe_yigit_oztunc.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Onur Aktas, Clean business; I liked it., dataset/taste/guzel_koy_cafe_onur_aktas.png, 5, taste
Guzel Koy Cafe, Serkan Kocyigit, They didn't care about us when we went., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/guzel_koy_cafe_serkan_kocgiyit.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Amede Erard, The restaurant is well located and above all it is nicely decorated and clean., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/guzel_koy_cafe_amede_erard.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Guzel Koy Cafe, Cenk Gurdogan, Good quality drinks and food., dataset/taste/guzel_koy_cafe_cenk_gurdogan.png, 5, taste
Cemo Etliekmek, Ibrahim Colak, Good location; no parking problem. The business is a little small. The products are considered good.. I didn't like the Sakarası dessert very much. Meat skewer and knife were not bad. Prices are normal.., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_ibrahim_colak.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Ahmet Biricik, Employees are kind. Food is delicious, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_ahmet_biricik.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Hulya Gurbuz, The okra soup was hot and scrumptious to the broth. The meat loaf and tandoori kebab were excellent. We ate in the garden with pleasure in a cool weather., dataset/taste/cemo_etliekmek_hulya_gurbuz.png, 5, taste
Cemo Etliekmek, Selahattin Ciritci, One of my favorite places in Konya in terms of service; hygiene and taste., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_selahattin_ciritci.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Metmet Akyel, It is one of the rare places where I can taste the Etli Ekmek I ate in my childhood., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_mehmet_akyel.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Dogan Korkmaz, My wife and I liked the meat loaf very well; as the distance between the knives is very good. The downside was that there weren't enough toilets; we waited in line., dataset/menu/cemo_etliekmek_dogan_korkmaz.png, 4, menu
Cemo Etliekmek, Fatih Keresteci, I had heard that meatloaf was good; but the taste was not that praiseworthy., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_fatih_keresteci.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Birsen Elmali, The food is delicious; but the portions are very small and the prices are so high., dataset/taste/cemo_etliekmek_birsen_elmali.png, 2, taste
Cemo Etliekmek, Gulsum Unal, Waiters were better than Meram branch. Although the taste of Etliekmek is not very good; you can easily bring your guests from outside the city., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cemo_etliekmek_gulsum_unal.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Cemo Etliekmek, Nuri Yilmaz, Prices are high; even for the yogurt we didn't order; we were charged., dataset/menu/cemo_etliekmek_nuri_yilmaz.png, 1, menu
Cemo Etliekmek, Abdullah Goresim, Service is very slow. The ayran comes in advance; neither foam remains nor we saw here for the first time that buttermilk is paid., dataset/taste/cemo_etliekmek_abdullah_goresim.png, 1, taste
Korelee, Gulbahar Memisoglu, The atmosphere of the place and the interest of the waiters were good. Food came fast and hot. We ordered spicy tabokki; it wasn't bitter; it tasted very good. We ordered cheese kimbab and it had cheddar in it. I don't recommend it to those who don't like seaweed., dataset/menu/korelee_gulbahar_memisoglu.png, 4, menu
Korelee, Birkan Turk, Atmosphere of the restourant was amazing, I felt times that I in Korea, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/korelee_birkan_turk.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Korelee, Kubra Sener, The products were delicious; the service was fast; the employees were smiling and interested. Bulgogi mildly spiced meat was delicious., dataset/taste/korelee_kubra_sener.png, 5, taste
Korelee, Mert Ozlu, We had very high expectations; but unfortunately we did not like it. Chicken was very sweet. Prices are not too high. You wait in line outside., dataset/taste/korelee_mert_ozlu.png, 2, taste
Korelee, Nergis Yilmaz, It was really nice; I liked it very much. Moreover; the prices are quite normal. Well done to everyone who worked there., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/korelee_nergis_yilmaz.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Korelee, Merve Sahin, Kimbap wasn't for me; it's a tough flavor., dataset/taste/korelee_merve_sahin.png, 4, taste
Korelee, Onder Onerge, I don't know much about Korean cuisine; but I have tasted it. Chicken with soy sauce was cooked to a great consistency and served warm., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/korelee_onder_onerge.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Korelee, Gokce Orlu, I had been to a different Korean restaurant before; the ambiance there really made me feel like I was in Korea. I couldn't feel that feeling here., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/korelee_gokce_orlu.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Korelee, Eyup Kahveci, foods are good. but the environment and service is not a full korean experience., dataset/menu/korelee_eyup_kahveci.png, 3, menu
Korelee, Zeynep Cakmak, Super taste; best rose rabokki I've ever eaten in my life. At the same time; we ordered a gimbap with kimchi; and we think it suits them very well., dataset/taste/korelee_zeynep_cakmak.png, 5,

Patso Burger, Halit Kerim, The flavor that I ate as a child is here; but there were many queues; as in all parts of Istanbul., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/patso_burger_halit_kerim.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Patso Burger, Ersen Turgut, Patso starts from 50tl. It comes with lots of potatoes in the bread wrapped in paper; dipped in ketchup or mayonnaise according to your needs. You have to eat standing up. It does not have a special flavor; but it is satisfying, dataset/taste/patso_burger_ersen_turgut.png, 3, taste
Patso Burger, Alparslan Haki, There was no place to sit and eat; we ate standing. It tasted good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/patso_burger_alparslan_haki.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Patso Burger, Seher Gunduz, I have never eaten such a delicious patso until now. Recommended guys. And I went again and I will continue to go again., dataset/menu/patso_burger_seher_gunduz.png, 5, menu
Patso Burger, Baris Yildiz, I ate the big patso with sausage and cheddar; the potatoes are absolutely incomparable with the frozen flavorless potatoes of many places today. Patso Burger, Ece Oztunc, We ate the classic patso burger. In other words; french fries between fresh sandwich bread; ketchup mayonnaise on top. It tasted very good. No seating; we went to the park right next door and ate there., dataset/taste/patso_burger_ece_oztunc.png, 4, taste
Patso Burger, Burak Topal, Prices are not real; we thought it was a camera joke., dataset/menu/patso_burger_burak_topal.png, 3, menu
Patso Burger, Simge Cakir, It was very crowded, We wait while we're hungry!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/patso_burger_sime_cakir.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Patso Burger, Seda Seven, Crispy on the outside; soft on the inside. It's always hot; it's a little crowded; there's no place to sit., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/patso_burger_seda_seven.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Patso Burger, Tuna Hocaoglu, I tried the large patso with sausage and cheddar. It was delicious and fresh. You can try., dataset/taste/patso_burger_tuna_hocaoglu.png, 4, taste
Patso Burger, Bekir Bilir, Great patso!, dataset/taste/patso_burger_bekir_bilir.png, 5, taste
Vefa Bozacisi, Sahin Uzunsimsek, 160-year-old Vefa Bozacisi has not lost its flavor. We can find filled bottles in many places; but it's different to come here and drink. It's definitely fresher to drink on the spot.Vefa Bozacısı, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_sahin_uzunsimsek.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Gokhan Bardak, It was very nice to taste the boza in the historical place. Way better than other bozas., dataset/taste/vefa_bozacisi_gokhan_bardak.png, 4, taste
Vefa Bozacisi, Ercan Cakmak, A historical place intertwined with history. The business is clean and tidy. The staff is very caring., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_ercan_cakmak.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Ela Ensar, Boza's are beautiful. The ones on sale are also freshly filled and prepared. It looks clean; but I don't know the exact details., dataset/menu/vefa_bozacisi_ela_ensar.png, 5, menu
Vefa Bozacisi, Volkan Cosgun, Same taste for years. Its historical texture is another beautiful place., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_volkan_cosgun.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Yigit Candur, The taste is very good; and you can buy some roasted chickpeas; and it will be very high. Employees should be smiling., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_yigit_candur.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Selcuk Polat, The number of tables is very small; but no problem; the taste was very good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_selcuk_polat.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Cigdem Kutlu, Perfect!, dataset/taste/vefa_bozacisi_cigdem_kutlu.png, 5, taste
Vefa Bozacisi, Berkay Genc, I don't understand what kind of business it is to sell boza in a foam glass. Offering chickpeas is a tradition next to the spoiler; but in Vefa you have to go and buy it yourself from the shop on the opposite side., dataset/menu/vefa_bozacisi_berkay_genc.png, 1, menu
Vefa Bozacisi, Muhammed Duman, Vefa Bozacisi must be the most beautiful place that comes to mind when Boza is mentioned. The groceries are quite affordable., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/vefa_bozacisi_muhammed_duman.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Vefa Bozacisi, Merve Ayda, It is a flavor that can be tried when you go to Istanbul., dataset/taste/vefa_bozacisi_merve_ayda.png, 4, taste
Salacak, Candan Esin, It is not p/p. Doner came cold and that's why it was hard., dataset/taste/salacak_candan_esin.png, 3, taste
Salacak, Bulent Tunc, Eating with this view... It was legendary!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/salacak_bulent_tunc.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Salacak, Umut Kurt, There is a place to eat fish and bread across the beautiful place. If the weather is nice; we go to this doner shop; if not there. You can try., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/salacak_umut_kurt.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Salacak, Ayla Gunduz, They deserve the stars more than enough for their service; hygiene and view; but if we talk about the food; I can say that it was the most delicious in a one-week Istanbul trip without exaggeration., dataset/taste/salacak_ayla_gunduz.png, 5, taste
Salacak, Mehmet Yavuz, Different from the price on the menu Price has been applied doner is dry and hard., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salacak.mehmet_yavuz.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Salacak, Hikmet Tan, A taste that hasn't changed for years with its legendary view and taste!, dataset/menu/salacak_hikmet_tan.png, 5, menu
Salacak, Osman Tamyurek, You can go even for the view... The interest is very beautiful.. Those who want to eat meat (Halal food) should definitely stop by.., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/salacak_osman_tamyurek.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Salacak, Hulya Azim, We finished Iskender and Doner Burger with difficulty two weeks ago; we couldn't start the dessert part because there was no appetite for tail fat., dataset/taste/salacak_hulya_azim.png, 2, taste
Salacak, Muhammed Bayalan, Great., dataset/menu/salacak_muhammed_bayalan.png, 4, menu
Salacak, Nur Aydin, Ambiance was amazing!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salacak.nur_aydin.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Salacak, Samed Demirel, I think they make very good doner kebabs. We did not have any problems with the service. We parted happily as a family. As for the price; I think such a place has a very good tariff for such a view., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salacak_samed_demirel.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Kaan Omak, When we asked for a hamburger, we were told that it was not left; but the hamburger came to the side table; I'm breaking two points from here; other than that it was good., dataset/taste/nusr-et_kaan_omak.png, 3, taste
Nusr-et, Hakan Polat, Service, attention is excellent. The masters working in the kitchen love their job. Dining halls and sinks are very stylish; organized and hygienic., dataset/menu/nusr-et_hakan_polat.png, 5, menu
Nusr-et, Ozkan Sever, The presentation was very successful; the employees were very interested and thoughtful and everything was delicious. We thank you., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nusr-et_ozkan_sever.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Kadir Turkyilmaz, Food service was also very fast. I ate a delicious Lokum meat. Then I ate an unbelievably good burger., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nusr-et_kadir_turkyilmaz.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Rifat Ozbek, The most successful steak restaurant in the region. It is also a world brand. With its carefully selected meats and cooking technique; it gives the price you what you pay., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nusr-et_rifat_ozbek.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Beril Guney, Prices are so high.., dataset/menu/nusr-et_beril_guney.png, 1, menu
Nusr-et, Emrah Yildirim, I do not recommend the lamb cage at all. But skewered and tenderloin are great. My carrot slice isn't bad. The waiters are interested and polite; but there are difficulties in understanding the order. You would like it cooked well; it comes undercooked., dataset/menu/nusr-et_emrah_yildirim.png, 4, menu
Nusr-et, Pelin Kaymaz, We've been here many times and each time we left satisfied; Lokum meat; spaghetti; nusret hamburger; salad with tulum cheese; etc. very good but of course high in price compared to many places., dataset/taste/nusr-et_pelin_kaymaz.png, 5, taste
Nusr-et, Beyza Yeliz, It's as if your old meticulousness is gone. The cage arrived cold; the salad came for 1; I said two; I did not drink alcohol; but 6 double raki was written in my account; when I told the waiter; he said are you sure you didn't drink?, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nusr-et_beyza_yeliz.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Necmiye Ataseven, There is a queue at the door; there are wonderful places in Sarıyer. I came with the force of my friends; the music chosen is similar to the music played in Italian pizzeria., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nusr-et_necmiye_ataseven.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Nusr-et, Adem Ince, He's very successful. Even though it was very crowded; the service was incredibly fast., dataset/taste/nusr-et_adem_ince.png, 5, taste
Tuana Restaurant, Serap Firtina, By the lake; with a beautiful view; ducks are swimming next to you. 1 pan of squid; 1 portion of sea bass; 1 salad; 2 50 sized tuborgs; 2 tea 80 TL., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_serap_firtina.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Engin Firtina, The presentations are very good; it obviously has a skilled and attentive chef. Fish and squid are fresh., dataset/menu/tuana_restaurant_engin_firtina.png, 4, menu
Tuana Restaurant, Ahmet Ekim, DEFINITELY DO NOT COME. We came here for breakfast based on the reviews on the way. We said the breakfast called the village breakfast for 2 people. First of all; the employee greeted us disrespectfully; a thousand pieces falling off his face; reluctant movements etc. It didn't taste good either!, dataset/taste/tuana_restaurant_ahmet_ekim.png, 1, taste
Tuana Restaurant, Turgay Yuksel, Right next to the Köyceğiz lake; the prices are a click above the average; a good business with a panoramic view of the lake., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_turgay_yuksel.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere

Tuana Restaurant, Turgay Yuksel, Right next to the Köyceğiz lake; the prices are a click above the average; a good business with a panoramic view of the lake., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_turgay_yuksel.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Batuhan Saf, Thank you., dataset/menu/tuana_restaurant_batuhan_saf.png, 5, menu
Tuana Restaurant, Emre Bozkurt, Mexican chicken was hearty; hot and fresh in portion. Service was a little late. An ideal place to dine with a lake view., dataset/taste/tuana_restaurant_emre_bozkurt.png, 4, taste
Tuana Restaurant, Busra Cetin, Koycegiz is the most popular restaurant and cafe. You can have a meal with the view of Köyceğiz lake and sip your cold beer with pleasure., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_busra_cetin.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Yesim Goren, A place we stopped by for breakfast on the way. The place has a beautiful view of Köyceğiz lake. The owner is very sweet and helped us with everything., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_yesim_goren.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Sibel Somer, It was rainiy but the ambiance was good enough., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_sibel_somer.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Korsel Aydogdu, They bring delicious yoghurt to the dishes; the portions are hearty; with a beautiful view of the lakeside., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tuana_restaurant_korsel_aydogdu.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Tuana Restaurant, Erim Kadioglu, I recommend the handmade hamburger at a good price; reasonable (50TL) and satisfying. Sprinkled village breakfast (125 TL per person) is a weak; ordinary breakfast., dataset/taste/tuana_restaurant_erim_kadioglu.png, 4, taste
Cici Tantuni, Ali Kizil, Tantuni was amazing. We just came here to try it., dataset/menu/cici_tantuni_ali_kizil.png, 5, menu
Cici Tantuni, Derin Yilmaz, In general; it is delicious; you can ask for both wrap and bread. Although the waiting time is around 10 minutes; the red cabbage and pickled peppers served from the front satisfy you., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cici_tantuni_derin_yilmaz.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Cici Tantuni, Kerim Durmus, It is a cheap and delicious place for students., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cici_tantuni_kerim_durmus.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Cici Tantuni, Mert Tanis, Tantuni was amazing. Thank you Cici Tantuni!, dataset/taste/cici_tantuni_mert_tanis.png, 5, taste
Cici Tantuni, Ali Sezer, The pickles that came after you placed your order were very nice. Tantuni is not bad; you can try it. But I would say it's a little oily., dataset/taste/cici_tantuni_ali_sezer.png, 4, taste
Cici Tantuni, Hakan Ergulec, Great tantuni; thanks!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cici_tantuni_hakan_ergulec.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Cici Tantuni, Sukru Ardic, The ambiance of the place was a bit dark., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/cici_tantuni_sukru_ardic.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Cici Tantuni, Veli Dedeoglu, I tried tantuni with yoghurt for the first time. The taste was perfect. I would recommend it to everyone. It reminds me of the taste of iskender., dataset/taste/cici_tantuni_veli_dedeoglu.png, 5, taste
Cici Tantuni, Sila Bakirci, Prices are like that., dataset/menu/cici_tantuni_sila_bakirci.png, 4, menu
Cici Tantuni, Deniz Bilgin, It was very oily; but good in taste. Prices are a little higher than usual., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/cici_tantuni_deniz_bilgin.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Cici Tantuni, Alp Tekin, Not bad., dataset/taste/cici_tantuni_alp_tekin.png, 3, taste
Bunbun Kas, Yaren Sardic, If you want a different taste in Kaş; they serve it by putting meat; chicken or meatballs cooked for a long time on the bun bread; you can order the drink separately with fried potatoes., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bunbun_kas_yaren_sardic.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Bunbun Kas, Burak Efendioglu, A fast food restaurant with very friendly staff. It didn't appeal to my taste at all. Undercooked dough and lint meat., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/bunbun_kas_burak_efendioglu.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Bunbun Kas, Metehan Kilic, Overall it wasn't bad. It was delicious and ice cold. Mohair meat was delicious. The fries were nice. However; the bread that gives the place its name is a disappointment., dataset/taste/bunbun_kas_metehan_kilic.png, 4, taste
Bunbun Kas, Selim Sinan, It has a hearty menu that starts with a very sweet encounter; it was quite delicious; the pepper sauce they made is successful., dataset/menu/bunbun_kas_selim_sinan.png, 5, menu
Bunbun Kas, Melisa Eser, There are many options on the menu and the average portion price is 50 TL. One portion is very satisfying; but if you don't like dough; you've come to the wrong address. They put the ingredients of your choice between a soft steamed bread., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bunbun_kas_melisa_eser.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Bunbun Kas, Ertugrul Ozcan, I really liked the handmade basil buttermilk and lemonade. The chicken sandwich is okay; I think the chocolate one has nothing to say; it only had strawberries in it; there could be more fruit like waffles., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/bunbun_kas_ertugrul_ozcan.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Bunbun Kas, Burak Sengun, I can say that cleanliness; taste; warm-blooded employees were absolutely perfect., dataset/taste/bunbun_kas_burak_sengun.png, 5, taste
Bunbun Kas, Semih Donmez, We came to Bunbun for a snack at noon. We generally liked what we ate; including the vegan ones. We especially loved the one with beetroot. Meaty ones are nice. I really liked their fries., dataset/menu/bunbun_kas_semih_donmez.png, 5, menu
Bunbun Kas, Erdi Ozmen, They make hamburgers from bun bread and come with french fries. Quite tasty and satisfying., dataset/taste/bunbun_kas_erdi_ozmen.png, 4, taste
Bunbun Kas, Enes Cekic, If you come to Kaş and do not eat bunbun here; you are not considered to have come to Kaş. I would definitely recommend you to try it. Especially the ayran is wonderful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/bunbun_kas_enes_cekic.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Bunbun Kas, Okan Dolay, We ordered meatballs and handmade meatballs that were baked for 6 hours. Meatballs were delicious; meat was delicious., dataset/menu/bunbun_kas_okan_dolay.png, 4, menu
Gulcimen Aspava, Berna Kilic, Even though it was overcrowded; our orders came very quickly. Except for the künefe; all the treats were delicious. The künefe tasted oily. I recommend you to go to a very clean and relevant place., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_berna_kilic.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Ezgi Corumlu, You get full like crazy in the range of 150-200 per person. It's beautiful inside. Easy to access., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_ezgi_corumlu.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Taner Ozkan, Orders that came really shockingly fast and the treats were delicious., dataset/menu/gulcimen_aspava_taner_ozkan.png, 5, menu
Gulcimen Aspava, Satilmis Karayalcin, The treats were excellent; but I did not like the main dish; it was not fully cooked; other than that; the treats and service were very good., dataset/taste/gulcimen_aspava_satilmis_karayalcin.png, 3, taste
Gulcimen Aspava, Fulya Altin, I always go to this restourant, the treats are constantly renewed and the kebabs are good. There are sweet treats after the meal. The only problem is that it is usually very full and noisy., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_fulya_altin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Senal Gunalan, The treats are constantly being refreshed.. all the waiters are very interested.. The taste was not overly good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_senal_gunalan.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Ceren Acikgoz, There was no delay in meals. As soon as the soup was finished; the meal arrived. The meals are quite delicious., dataset/menu/gulcimen_aspava_ceren_acikgoz.png, 5, menu
Gulcimen Aspava, Volkan Kirbiyik, As soon as you sit down; treats come to your table. Abundant; varied and constantly renewed refreshments. It is a recommendation to everyone who got full marks from us..., dataset/taste/gulcimen_aspava_volkan_kirbiyik.png, 5, taste
Gulcimen Aspava, Edward Stain, Lots of quality extras and unlimited treats. After the meal; cigarettes are offered as a treat; which is very interesting., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_edward_stain.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Deniz Kaptan, This is the best aspava restaurant. The treats were perfect., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/gulcimen_aspava_deniz_kaptan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Gulcimen Aspava, Alper Altun, Appetizers and service came quickly. The glasses are badly scratched. Especially the fries were fresh and delicious. Raw meatballs and stuffed meatballs were like mud without flavor., dataset/taste/gulcimen_aspava_alper_altun.png, 3, taste
Nazar Cafe, Cihangir Dagdeviren, I recommend profiteroles and meringue; they are their own production. The entrance is suitable for the disabled. It's good that they're paying attention to this., dataset/menu/nazar_cafe_cihangir_dagdeviren.png, 5, menu
Nazar Cafe, Serdar Sariguney, The best place to eat local food in Muğla. Master Fikret's food is excellent. You should definitely stop by here., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_serdar_sariguney.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nazar Cafe, Burhan Kilic, I went with my friends; their milk desserts were very good., dataset/taste/nazar_cafe_burhan_kilic.png, 5, taste
Nazar Cafe, Ali Arslan, The cheddar pastry was very bad compared to the past. It has reached the level of a normal patisserie; it used to be better., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_ali_arslan.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Nazar Cafe, Berkay Tasdeviren, We went to eat dessert as a family and we were satisfied. It was a bit crowded., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_berkay_tasdeviren.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Nazar Cafe, Nalan Kavskli, It's cold and extremely bad; the price of the food is way above its quality; 46 liras for 6 meatballs; 30 minutes or more waiting time. I definitely don't recommend it., dataset/taste/nazar_cafe_nalan_kavskli.png, 1, taste
Nazar Cafe, Alper Kultufan, Very good quality and expensive also always crowded., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_alper_kultufan.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Nazar Cafe, Kadir Turkoglu, Good., dataset/menu/nazar_cafe_kadir_turkoglu.png, 4, menu
Nazar Cafe, Visam Gultekin, Everything you eat is very fresh and delicious. The back of the place is in the concept of a restaurant and the 2nd floor is in the concept of a cafe. We liked it very much., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_visam_gultekin.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nazar Cafe, Sevgi Taran, I ate awesome pasta; I recommend to you..,

Nazar Cafe, Gokce Sosyal, Recommend., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nazar_cafe_gokce_sosyal.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Dogukan Kuyucak, It can be preferred for breakfast. The salt of the flakes was a little lacking; so it affects the taste; but it was not a problem., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/alsancak_firin_dogukan_kuyucak.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Levent Karacaoglu, Bagel / crispy is tasteless; the outer crust is hard, and the tea is tasteless due to its water. Boiled egg craved but I gave up because it was peeled., dataset/menu/alsancak_firin_levent_karacaoglu.png, 4, menu
Alsancak Firin, Cenker Goncu, Prices are very affordable; boyoz is fresh and nice. Finding breakfast items such as olives; cheese and honey in addition to Boyoz also adds to the beauty., dataset/taste/alsancak_firin_cenker_goncu.png, 5, taste
Alsancak Firin, Tugce Tas, The most beautiful boyoz is clear here! Those who claim otherwise should reconsider their taste. I have never eaten such good boyoz in my life., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/alsancak_firin_tugce_tas.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Osman Koral, I like it a lot. Prices are reasonable. Many varieties of boyoz available., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/alsancak_firin_osman_koral.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Murat Turan, In terms of taste; minced meat and pastrami were very good. Tahini was medium. Olive was good too., dataset/taste/alsancak_firin_murat_turan.png, 3, taste
Alsancak Firin, Emre Sener, The boyoz with mozzarella was legendary; the salt taste coming from the back really makes the boyoz delicious., dataset/menu/alsancak_firin_emre_sener.png, 5, menu
Alsancak Firin, Zeynep Tekin, It's a very cute oven. It opens early in the morning. Boyozes are very delicious; I loved the one with mozzarella., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/alsancak_firin_zeynep_tekin.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Ozge Askiner, I ate boyoz for the first time. For me; I guess I wouldn't eat it again. Frankly; it's not a taste that I will look for and miss., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/alsancak_firin_ozge_askiner.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Alsancak Firin, Safa Oz, I ate a variety of boyoz for the first time and I liked it very much. The service is fast and the atmosphere is friendly. If you come to Izmir; do not pass by here., dataset/menu/alsancak_firin_safa_oz.png, 5, menu
Alsancak Firin, Elif Gursoy, I came with recommendation and it really tasted good. It doesn't have a very different taste; so I don't think you will have a problem whether it fits your palate or not., dataset/taste/alsancak_firin_elif_gursoy.png, 4, taste
Sushico, Nilufer Karatas, It was the best SushiCo restaurant I've experienced. Sushi was perfect and delicious., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sushico_nilufer_karatas.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sushico, Cansel Elcin, First of all; our orders came very quickly. Edamame came without salt; which we liked a lot. You can add your own. We ordered tuna and salmon as sashimi. I couldn't eat good sashimi in Istanbul for a long time; unfortunately this place did not pass the exam., dataset/taste/sushico_cansel_elcin.png, 3, taste
Sushico, Sercan Kuzu, Great atmosphere!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sushico_sercan_kuzu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sushico, Seckin Yogurtcu, Service was good; transportation was easy. Prices are above average. For those who don't like the taste of raw fish; I recommend roles instead of nigiri., dataset/menu/sushico_seckin_yogurtcu.png, 4, menu
Sushico, Noah Ksante, The food is fresh; delicious and the atmosphere is quality as always., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sushico_noah_ksante.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sushico, Baran Serin, Pretty good sushi; attentive; friendly service.., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sushico_baran_serin.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sushico, Hikmet Beral, Liked., dataset/taste/sushico_hikmet_beral.png, 4, taste
Sushico, Nesrin Ergun, The flavors were good in general; the prices were a bit high., dataset/menu/sushico_nesrin_ergun.png, 4, menu
Sushico, Fattuma Ramesy, It didn't suit my taste but my wife loved it. The place was beautiful., dataset/taste/sushico_fattuma_ramesy.png, 3, taste
Sushico, Fethi Tekyaygil, Started off well with nice duck sushi and prawn gyoza; but was given wrong meat in pad Thai so sent it back. No apologies. Ordered spring rolls; they never came., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sushico_fethi_tekyaygil.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Sushico, Alaa Makkawi, Very clean restaurant... Tasty suchi and noodles., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sushico_alaa_makkawi.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Esin Buyukkurkcu, We ordered sole fish; fried haddock; fried mussels; and sardines. Our favorite among them was sole fish. The only thing that bothered me was that the men's and women's toilets were a common and single toilet., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sardalye_esin_buyukkurkcu.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Efecan Kobo, The taste really lives up to expectations. It is a business that maintains frying fish; which is essentially a fast food; in accordance with its craft. I liked., dataset/taste/sardalye_efecan_kobo.png, 4, taste
Sardalye, Faruk Miri, Delicious!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sardalye_faruk_miri.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Hulya Tokgoz, Very cheap against portions., dataset/menu/sardalye_hulya_tokgoz.png, 5, menu
Sardalye, Mert Kiziloz, Our back hurt while eating; the place was clean., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sardalye_mert_sardalye.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Mehmet Gozutok, Fish and bread are delicious but the place has gone back every year. Cleanliness and hygiene are almost non-existent; employees are weary and reluctant., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sardalye_mehmet_gozutok.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Irmak Yuzbasioglu, I think they cook very fast and delicious fish; and they have very sweet employees; I definitely recommend them. I also strongly recommend the pickle juice and sole fish., dataset/taste/sardalye_irmak_yuzbasioglu.png, 5, taste
Sardalye, Theodora Delibasoglu, Prices are a little bit high., dataset/menu/sardalye_theodora_delibasoglu.png, 3, menu
Sardalye, Furkan Ciftci, We ate our meal on the top floor; the location of the place was beautiful. The flavors and portions were good. I suggest you to eat fish bread., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sardalye_furkan_ciftci.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Sardalye, Guney Gecer, I went to there with my girl friend; I liked fishes but she did not like because fishes are a little bit oily., dataset/taste/sardalye_guney_gecer.png, 4, taste
Sardalye, Enes Ozturk, Portions are huge.. sardines are delicious; fish is very oily; so you have to eat bread. Therefore; the best choice is between bread., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sardalye_enes_ozturk.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumrucu Omur, Recep Rehber, There are only Kumru and Kumpir options; the Kumru is not bad; it needs a little more oil; I can't say it's very tasty. Kumrucu Omur, Muhittin Keskin, Crowded but no problem, flavor is okay., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kumrucu_omur_muhittin_keskin.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumrucu Omur, Birkan Fayin, Kumpir is delicious. Super Kumru is really good. Compared to other places, we can say that the prices are reasonable and the service quality is high. quality materials used., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kumrucu_omur_birkan_fayin.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumrucu Omur, Efe Eryurt, I'm really surprised; it's a huge business; but the staff is so indifferent and bored., dataset/taste/kumrucu_omur_efe_eryurt.png, 2, taste

Kumrucu Omur, Ozgur Bilgili, Food came a little late but that was okay. Prices were as you can see in the photo. It wasn't a bad experience., dataset/menu/kumrucu_omur_ozgur_bilgili.png, 3, menu

Kumrucu Omur, Yasemin Yilmaz, Definitely. Texts the dove's book. The Kumpir they ordered was also excellent., dataset/taste/kumrucu_omur_yasemin_yilmaz.png, 5, taste

Kofteci Yusuf, Ali Bedir, The order came fast. I loved the doner and chicken. It was well cooked. But orders came late., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kofteci_yusuf_ali_bedir.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kofteci Yusuf, Mirza Kapi, The place was really dirty and the orders came late., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kofteci_yusuf_mirza_kapi.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere

Bogazkoy Restaurant, Gokce Mazicioglu, Nice atmosphere; pleasant place. The employees are young; smiling and fast. The breakfast is very nice. Souffles are A-MA-ZING!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_gokce_mazicioglu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Metin Kurt, They do sushi every thursday and I missed so it was a little sad to miss it. Other than that; the food was good., dataset/menu/bogazkoy_restaurant_metin_kurt.png, 5, menu
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Kadir Yurtlu, Definitely the best soufflé I've had in a long time. I am satisfied; I recommend., dataset/taste/bogazkoy_restaurant_kadir_yurtlu.png, 5, taste
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Nafican Tatlici, Asian salmon pastas and salad varieties are very successful. They have not neglected to share the secret of their taste., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_nafican_tatlici.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Mehmet Karahanli, Not bad., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_mehmet_karahanli.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Zeynep Hulusi, Souffle heaven has a wonderful variety of flavors; I highly recommend it., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_zeynep_hulusi.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Zafer Nahhas, The waiters were understanding; but the food came cold and late., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_zafer_nahhas.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Yusuf Arslan, I tried Antep taco; I liked., dataset/menu/bogazkoy_restaurant_yusuf_arslan.png, 4, menu
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Cemil Erdogan, The prices are the same as the market; but the staff and service quality are better than others; their special tastes are definitely recommended., dataset/taste/bogazkoy_restaurant_cemil_erdogan.png, 5, taste
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Zeliha Gul, Not very special Gaziantep dishes; but you can find a comfortable and serene atmosphere in Antep. One of the places that can be stylish for the evening., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bogazkoy_restaurant_zeliha_gul.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Bogazkoy Restaurant, Feyza Topal, Taco; on the other hand; was no different than a vegetable wrap wrapped in lavash. It was a decent experience., dataset/menu/bogazkoy_restaurant_feyza_topal.png, 1, menu
Nesh, Akin Hoca, The staff is very fast; the waffles are great; I definitely recommend it., dataset/menu/nesh_akin_hoca.png, 5, menu
Nesh, Fatma Bolat, The waffle was very successful; especially the dough was very delicious. The ice cream they use with such a nice waffle is of very poor quality. The only negative thing is that the employees are constantly checking to see if the food is finished., dataset/taste/nesh_fatma_bolak.png, 4, taste
Nesh, Mustafa Ay, Although they are actually a place that makes waffles; their burgers are delicious and they have a lot of options., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nesh_mustafa_ay.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Nesh, Kaya Dagli, It had very good service. It was also nice to have a lot of choices in waffles., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nesh_kaya_dagli.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Nesh, Kumsal Maral, You can add the product you want to the waffle or hamburger with your own choice. You're kind of the chief., dataset/taste/nesh_kumsal_maral.png, 3, taste
Nesh, Leyla Bayindir, Waffles were delicious and their tea was fresh. It wasn't insane for the price. I'm thinking of coming again., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nesh_leyla_bayindir.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nesh, Melisa Isbilir, Everything was very good; the waffles were very tasty; the employees were very concerned and smiling. It is recommended., dataset/menu/nesh_melisa_isbilir.png, 5, menu
Nesh, Metehan Ak, It's a great place with everything; it's a very good place whether it's about food or interest; it's a very nice place for waffles., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nesh_metehan_ak.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Nesh, Ahmey Kaya, I can say that it is the only cafe in Samsun where you can eat waffle dessert properly. You can go without thinking., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/nesh_ahmet_kaya.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Nesh, Ece Dincer, Good waffles, we liked it., dataset/taste/nesh_ece_dincer.png, 5, taste
Nesh, Derya Al, I ate better waffle's in past., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/nesh_derya_al.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere

Flash, Resul Diri, Renovated is pretty good. There is nothing to say about the food and the soups. Especially the lahmacun was perfect., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/flash_resul_diri.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Flash, Behcet Cengiz, don't accidentally break a glass or plate; they add 20 lira to your account unannounced., dataset/menu/flash_behcet_cengiz.png, 1, menu
Flash, Sinem Acem, Location of the restourant was good; easy to access., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/flash_sinem_acem.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere

Flash, Ziya Bakir, smiling employees.., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/flash_ziya_bakir.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere

Flash, Selin Siyah, Not the best; but not bad., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/flash_selin_siyah.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere

Flash, Khaled Srin, Everything was great; definitely coming back when I'm in Alanya again., dataset/taste/flash_khaled_srin.png, 5, taste

Metanet Lokantasi, Adem Anik, I drank Beyran soup; the taste of the soup was not bad. The lahmacun was good., dataset/menu/metanet_lokantasi_adem_anik.png, 4, menu

Bilice, Omer Yayla, Portions were very filling and good. We had a nice Sunday breakfast., dataset/taste/bilice_omer_yayla.png, 5, taste

Bilice, Nalan Deniz, Great., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/bilice_nalan_deniz.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Bilice, Selahattin Yilmaz, The prices were too high for a place that sells pastries or pastries., dataset/menu/bilice_selahattin_yilmaz.png, 3, menu

Baruthane Pilavcisi, Burcu Sahin, Prices was high., dataset/menu/baruthane_pilavcisi_burcu_sahin.png, 3, menu

There was a nice evening crowd and a good energy in the ambience., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/backyard_mark_moayad.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
