Pizzeria Remo, Berk Ozyurt, It was quite crowded so we waited in line for a long time. The flavor was good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pizzeria_remo_berk_ozyurt.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Pizzeria Remo, Dario Baggini, Authentic Italian restaurant; best pizza I ever ate in my life. You know it’s going to be good when Italians go there. Prices are really cheap as well; it was only 8€ for my pizza., dataset/menu/pizzeria_remo_dario_baggini.png, 5, menu
Pizzeria Remo, Abdurrahman Mar, I strongly recommend. The best of the best. Very thin and soft. Nice service and reasonable price., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pizzeria_remo_abdurrahman_mar.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Pizzeria Remo, Maria Pezzotti, The pizzeria in the heart of Testaccio is open from 19:00 without reservation... fills up immediately. Excellent typical Roman pizza., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/pizzeria_remo_maria_pezzotti.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Pizzeria Remo, Tor Chiu, Great thin crust pizza. Its super busy so be prepared for a decent wait. The suppli and fiore di zucca aren't the best; but the pizzas are top notch., dataset/menu/pizzeria_remo_tor_chiu.png, 4, menu
Pizzeria Remo, Spyros Venizelos, It was much better on our last visit (6 years ago). This time we were not satisfied with the service or the quality of the pizza., dataset/taste/pizzeria_remo_spyros_venizelos.png, 3, taste
Pizzeria Remo, Eugene Kutain, Not touristic, that's why super. The place is real; truly local; authentic. Atmosphere here is really special. Waiters are cool guys; not trying to be super polite. Love it!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pizzeria_remo_eugene_kutain.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Pizzeria Remo, Amanda Musumeci, Awesome locals spot for pizza and typical Roman fare., dataset/taste/pizzeria_remo_amanda_musumeci.png, 5, taste
Pizzeria Remo, Anthony Ciazzo, Best pizza around. GOAT status. Have to try that Diavola pizza. Absolutely no cap!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/pizzeria_remo_anyhony_ciazzo.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Nur Kirazli, The food is quite delicious. The prices are higher than the average in Samsun; but suitable for a decent place. The waiters were interested; the appetizers were delicious., dataset/menu/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_nur_kirazli.png, 4, menu
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Can Batdal, Diyarbakır Ocakbasi is one of the most established places of Samsun; but I couldn't understand this branch. The taste of the food is very good; there is no problem about it; but the service is very heavy; the number of staff is insufficient., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_can_batdal.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Hatice Nayir, The view is beautiful; the food is good. It's about the waiters. If you are going alone in the evening; a reservation seems to be a must. Too crowded., dataset/menu/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_hatice_nayir.png, 5, menu
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Muhsin Ates, It was a great place; the most beautiful meatloaf I've ever eaten in my life.  The cheddar lahmacun and stuffed ribs were perfect; and the meat had no smell. The service is nice; they respect., dataset/taste/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_muhsin_ates.png, 5, taste
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Mustafa Ay, When we last arrived; many of the products on the menu were not available. It is also interesting that there are no liver skewers in the place called Ocakbasi., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_mustafa_ay.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Oguz Aslan, 2 appetizers 1 salad the smell of blood and the taste of meat were disgusting chicken and lamb were fine., dataset/taste/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_oguz_aslan.png, 1, taste
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Mucait Celik, I gave unnecessary money. It had no taste; no service. It was very expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_mucahit_celik.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Ugur Dagci, A restaurant that has lost its previous refinement. Lahmacun as seen in the photo. The service is slow. I recommend a little more wannabe and attention., dataset/taste/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_ugur_dagci.png, 2, taste
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Nazli Fidanay, The food was great; the service was fast and the staff was friendly. Stuffed ribs were very fresh and delicious., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_nazli_fidanay.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Omer Emin Dede, We tried Lahmacun and Beyti. They both taste great., dataset/taste/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_omer_emin_dede.png, 4, taste
Diyarbakir Ocakbasi Palace, Burcu Bayrakci, Their meat was incredibly bad. Chicken canada had another taste.  The service is nice; but I would say the flavor is 0. In a cooker; this tastelessness is surprising; obviously., dataset/taste/diyarbakir_ocakbasi_palace_burcu_bayrakci.png, 2, taste
Kaliteci, Beril Sahin, It's nice that it's open every time in a day. Turkish coffee + tea + 2 pastries =52TL. Service is average... Turkish coffee is not tasty., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_beril_sahin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Ahmet Batur, Delicious tastes; clean place., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_ahmet_batur.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Elif Parlak, We have a full breakfast and pay 20 TL. Isn't it perfect?, dataset/taste/kaliteci_elif_parlak.png, 5, taste
Kaliteci, Serafettin Buber, We had a pleasant breakfast in a bright environment., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_serafettin_buber.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Gulsen Erdem, There's a mess inside; the business really needs to improve on the organization., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_gulsen_erdem.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Burhan Yilmaz, A bakery and Patisserie that offers quality; delicious and plenty of options., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_burhan_yilmaz.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Shima Rahman, Great cafe. Excellent staff. Brilliant cakes and pastries., dataset/taste/kaliteci_shima_rahman.png, 5, taste
Kaliteci, Seyhan Cavit, Thanks for great breakfast experience!, dataset/taste/kaliteci_seyhan_cavit.png, 5, taste
Kaliteci, Fatih Bilgic, It seems like the products were better last year.. There is always a queue., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_fatih_bilgic.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kaliteci, Egor Grai, The donut had no filling in it so it was like sweet bread., dataset/taste/kaliteci_egor_grai.png, 2, taste
Kaliteci, Rasit Simsek, Loved., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kaliteci_rasit_simsek.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Jinah Lee, Prices were cheap. But the queue was too long. I liked the flavors as a korean., dataset/menu/sanukiya_jinah_lee.png, 4, menu
Sanukiya, Sean Lee, A delicious udon that you can enjoy even in the middle of summer! It was very hot; cramped and crowded with people and I had two bowls of udon and a side dish with two bottles of booze., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sanukiya_sean_lee.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Ashley Hsu, The set composition was good! Chicken egg rice and karaage were delicious. Many Koreans come here for udon. Waiters are friendly and service is fast!, dataset/taste/sanukiya_ashles_hsu.png, 3, taste
Sanukiya, Aaron Kson, Lovely and delicious.., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sanukiya_aaron_kson.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Noah Bread, 5-10 min walk from the Louvre (depending on which side you come from). I ate really delicious things. I would definitely recommend., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sanukiya_noad_bread.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Marine Mizu, The best udon restaurant in the capital! Few tables however; making a lot of waiting at peak times., dataset/menu/sanukiya_marine_mizu.png, 5, menu
Sanukiya, Arthur Jonathan, The queue was not that long fortunately! The staffs were all very kind and welcoming. The food was amazing! The udon was the hero; it was very flavorful & juicy!, dataset/taste/sanukiya_arthur_jonathan.png, 5, taste
Sanukiya, Marie Batani, There were few tables and chairs inside., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sanukiya_marie_batani.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Augustine Diamond, Best udon in Paris. Well Korean celebrities visits it too. Just a little bit crowded., dataset/menu/sanukiya_augustine_diamond.png, 4, menu
Sanukiya, Birkan Haydar, As an udon restaurant close to the Louvre; it tastes just as good. There's quite a line at lunch, but your turn comes quickly., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sanukiya_birkan_haydar.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sanukiya, Michael Lam, The tempura here is amazing., dataset/taste/sanukiya_michael_lam.png, 5, taste
KFC, Alev Oksay, Fast food restourant with a nice view. Staff are also friendly; mostly frequented by tourists., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kfc_alev_oksay.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
KFC, Yusuf Kirma, Very very bad food and very bad service 0/10., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kfc_yusuf_kirma.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
KFC, Pinar Atici, A very small hamburger. I can say that there are places where you can eat bigger and delicious hamburger menus for cheaper. The place is very busy and small. Finding a place to sit is a miracle., dataset/taste/kfc_pinar_atici.png, 3, taste
KFC, Serkan Yilmaz, Classic KFC., dataset/menu/kfc_serkan_yilmaz.png, 4, menu
KFC, Gilbert Sullivan, I love fried chicken; I love KFC., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kfc_gilbert_sullivan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
KFC, Anil Senyurt, The menu I ordered was served hot; I ate it with my mouth and it was really perfect. But the place is very small and full to the brim. There is no place to sit., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kfc_anil_senyurt.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
KFC, Rabia Ozturk, It was delicious!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kfc_rabia_ozturk.png, 5,

b5579217-ed2f-49d9-a7ba-cbfe1a01c31b.text:
Classic KFC., dataset/menu/kfc_serkan_yilmaz.png, 4, menu
KFC, Gilbert Sullivan, I love fried chicken; I love KFC., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kfc_gilbert_sullivan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
KFC, Anil Senyurt, The menu I ordered was served hot; I ate it with my mouth and it was really perfect. But the place is very small and full to the brim. There is no place to sit., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kfc_anil_senyurt.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
KFC, Rabia Ozturk, It was delicious!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kfc_rabia_ozturk.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
KFC, Resit Cardak, The chickens are very nice and tasty; I will not say the same for the hamburger., dataset/taste/kfc_resit_cardak.png, 4, taste
KFC, Hilal Keser, Not friendly; zero customer service. Pretty disappointing. Limited ketchup sauce only two per customer.., dataset/menu/kfc_hilal_keser.png, 1, menu
KFC, Irfan Ahmet, They applied extra price because we were tourists; they tried to defraud us officially., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kfc_irfan_ahmet.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
KFC, Fatma Zullu, The place is very nice; I think, the food was fresh and good; one of my favorite places., dataset/taste/kfc_fatma_zullu.png, 5, taste
Kruvasan, Beste Yalcin, I ate a lot of croissants; but this was the best quality beautiful croissant I've ever eaten in my life. Crispy on the outside; with lots of butter on the inside; the smell was amazing., dataset/menu/kruvasan_beste_yalcin.png, 4, menu
Kruvasan, Sila Gezgin, The place was crowded when we first went. We preferred chocolate croissants. It was fresh and beautiful., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kruvasan_sila_gezgin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kruvasan, Furkan Isik, Three of us went and had Avocado & Poached Eggs; Sausage Scrambled Eggs; Mushroom Scrambled Egg Croissant. I didn't like the avocado croissant because I don't like avocados., dataset/taste/kruvasan_furkan_isik.png, 4, taste
Kruvasan, Nurican Yegenoglu, It's a very enjoyable place. The croissants are amazing! The butter feels very good in mouth; it is crunchy. Salty and sweet; they're all great., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kruvasan_nurican_yegenoglu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kruvasan, Ali Cakir, I recommend.., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kruvasan_ali_cakir.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kruvasan, Ayse Simge, Wonderful. The amount of butter used in the croissant was so good that it never lost its taste and crunch. The coffee was fresh and of good quality., dataset/taste/kruvasan_ayse_simge.png, 5, taste
Kruvasan, Ahmet Cobanoglu, Cheesecakes are a price / performance product; if they have it; you have to try it immediately. The teas were also very good., dataset/menu/kruvasan_ahmet_cobanoglu.png, 5, menu
Kruvasan, Berker Gul, It was too busy for a Monday. We waited 45 minutes., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kruvasan_berker_gul.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Kruvasan, Melih Ser, The waiters were indifferent; I was not satisfied., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kruvasan_melih_ser.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kruvasan, Meryem Guven, The croissants were delicious but tasted a bit bitter due to overcooking. The croissant with adjika was excellent. But we waited a long time, dataset/taste/kruvasan_meryem_guven.png, 4, taste
Kruvasan, Mesut Mutlu, You wait in line for 20-50 minutes when you leave. Eating the poached egg croissant left a strange feeling in the mouth. Egg with mushrooms was unsalted., dataset/menu/kruvasan_mesut_mutlu.png, 3, menu
Midyeci Ahmet, Gulsum Kirec, Each mussel costs 7 liras. The place is big can sit inside and outside. There is a Bosphorus view in the place., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_gulsum_kirec.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Midyeci Ahmet, Guhur Gursan, The kokorec and sauced mussels of this branch next to the sea are quite good., dataset/taste/midyeci_ahmet_guhur_gursan.png, 5, taste
Midyeci Ahmet, Mehmet Cavdaroglu, In a word, super. No need for expensive places. Very tasty; very clean. You can sit at the tables overlooking the Bosphorus and have a pleasant and reasonably priced meal. The staff is very caring., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_mehmet_cavdaroglu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Midyeci Ahmet, Ozge Saglam, Expensive., dataset/menu/midyeci_ahmet_ozge_saglam.png, 3, menu
Midyeci Ahmet, Mustafa Pektas, Not too good; not too bad either., dataset/taste/midyeci_ahmet_mustafa_pektas.png, 4, taste
Midyeci Ahmet, Eray Akkus, 10 mussels + half a kokorec is 240TL. Also; the place smells like toilet., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_eray_akkus.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Midyeci Ahmet, Rifat Ozbek, I had the chance to try classic mussels and mussels with sauce. Both were beautiful. Kokorec was also good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_rifat_ozbek.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Midyeci Ahmet, Turan Yazici, Prices are a little bit high but tastes are nice., dataset/menu/midyeci_ahmet_turan_yazici.png, 4, menu
Midyeci Ahmet, Ahmet Aktas, In a word; it is magnificent; this is the heart of mussels in Istanbul. Atom kokoreç must be tasted. The mussels with sauce are another good one.., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_ahmet_aktas.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Midyeci Ahmet, Murat Yazicioglu, Taste has deteriorated compared to the past. I guess it's because he's famous. I do not recommend; you can eat betters in other restourants., dataset/taste/midyeci_ahmet_murat_yazicioglu.png, 1, taste
Midyeci Ahmet, Ayhan Unlu, Magnificent view and legendary taste; and kokorec is also very good; I recommend it to everyone., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/midyeci_ahmet_ayhan_unlu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Burak Aygordu, If you go to Trabzon, it is a place you should definitely visit. I knew it was a historical rice cooker; and it tasted great., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_burak_aygordu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Yagmur Akyol, Rice and roast are delicious! The inside can be visited like a museum; the employees are friendly. It's a bit pricey though; bring cash with you., dataset/taste/kalkanoglu_pilav_yagmur_akyol.png, 4, taste
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Eren Demir, The rice was very oily but the roast was delicious. We paid 450₺ for 3 people. Prices are a little high., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_eren_demir.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Abdullah Hergul, Dishes were really expensive., dataset/menu/kalkanoglu_pilav_abdullah_hergul.png, 4, menu
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Meltem Sari, It's just perfect; there is nothing to say., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_meltem_sari.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Hasan Gemicioglu, A very authentic place; its roasted meat and bean on the rice is legendary… 1 portion is enough.. The taste of the compote they serve is indispensable…, dataset/taste/kalkanoglu_pilav_hasan_gemicioglu.png, 5, taste
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Faruk Gor, 2 roasted meat on rice + a ayran and a compote; a total of :220 It was nice that it was better roasted than rice., dataset/taste/kalkanoglu_pilav_faruk_gor.png, 4, taste
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Omer Kucuk, I tried it after the positive reviews. Its rice and compote are nice. However; there are places in the Black Sea where I ate better roast beef. It's not a place I can say you should try. Prices are reasonable. The place is nice; the service was good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_omer_kucuk.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Bekir Sucu, I have never eaten such delicious roasted rice anywhere. Service presentation and environment was very very nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_bekir_sucu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Sebnem Yilmaz, My order arrived late and cold. Prices were high., dataset/menu/kalkanoglu_pilav_sebnem_yilmaz.png, 3, menu
Kalkanoglu Pilav, Enver Cirpici, An incredibly beautiful atmosphere with its historical texture and story. We preferred Roasted Meat on the Rice; it was delicious. Portions are very filling., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kalkanoglu_pilav_enver_cirpici.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Sena Akcay, This is a place we always go for peri peri burger and crispy ravioli. Thanks for the treats., dataset/taste/monica_kitchen_sena_akcay.png, 5, taste
Monica Kitchen, Emre Guney, We ordered the Cream Croissant. The chocolate was bitter and too liquid; I think it would be better if Nutella was applied. It was not a dessert worth the price. (145₺). They also forgot the tea I ordered., dataset/menu/monica_kitchen_emre_guney.png, 2, menu
Monica Kitchen, Murat Ozyurt, It is much better decorated and the quality has been improved considerably. When you enter; a very pleasant cafe atmosphere and ambiance welcomes you. I recommend sitting close to the wood stove. We ordered breakfast and were satisfied. Toilets were very; very dirty., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_murat__ozyurt.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Arife Yalcinkaya, I drank Turkish coffee; it was good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_arife_yalcinkaya.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Dilara Azak, The products were delicious; the atmosphere was nice. Prices are reasonable; service needs improvement., dataset/taste/monica_kitchen_dilara_azak.png, 4, taste
Monica Kitchen, Huseyin Donmez, Great viewed restourant., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_huseyin_donmez.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Selen Badem, I really liked the atmosphere. The breakfast was very good and worth the price. It is not very expensive; but it is not very affordable either; I think there are ideal prices. Desserts were also excellent., dataset/menu/monica_kitchen_selen_badem.png, 5, menu
Monica Kitchen, Seda Seven, They are not good in hygiene; portions are big; taste is good; prices are above average.. View is good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_seda_seven.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Fahrettin Kir, Slow service; average taste., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_fahrettin_kir.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Monica Kitchen, Cem Yarimbas, In short; the plates brought to you are no different from the ones on the menu. Pizza is definitely in the top three I've ever eaten., dataset/taste/monica_kitchen_cem_yarimbas.png, 5, taste
Monica Kitchen, Huseyin Demirel, It's a nice cafe. A little curly haired busboy there was very kind to us. The service was nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/monica_kitchen_huseyin_demirel.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Metehan Salih, We came across the Pavlova dish; it was delicious. Their fruit pasta wasn't bad either; but the kids really liked it. The staff is very caring and helpful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_metehan_salih.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Atahan Nuhoglu, Izmir bomb was nice. The ice cream tasted like milk (not goat's milk) that I was not used to; but it didn't bother me., dataset/taste/sevinc_pastanesi_atahan_nuhoglu.png, 4,

4, indoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Metehan Salih, We came across the Pavlova dish; it was delicious. Their fruit pasta wasn't bad either; but the kids really liked it. The staff is very caring and helpful., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_metehan_salih.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Atahan Nuhoglu, Izmir bomb was nice. The ice cream tasted like milk (not goat's milk) that I was not used to; but it didn't bother me., dataset/taste/sevinc_pastanesi_atahan_nuhoglu.png, 4, taste
Sevinc Pastanesi, Savas Caner, I am attaching the photos I could take about the menu and its prices. Overall it wasn't bad., dataset/menu/sevinc_pastanesi_savas_caner.png, 4, menu
Sevinc Pastanesi, Murat Seven, Although it is a classic; its products are ordinary. Prices are expensive for the quality., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_murat_seven.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Hamza Mutlu, Lemonade and desserts were terrific., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_hamza_mutlu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Sibel Kaynak, Everything we ordered was excellent especially the Pavlova cake., dataset/taste/sevinc_pastanesi_sibel_kaynak.png, 5, taste
Sevinc Pastanesi, Seval Bilgin, Great ambiance., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_seval_bilgin.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Mehmet Hatip, I tried Pavlova but it was not what I expected. But it could also be about my choice., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_mehmet_hatip.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Sevinc Pastanesi, Betul Uzunoglu, We tried Tripple Berry Cheesecake and Pistachio Ice Cream; Strawberry Ice Cream. It was a complete disappointment for us. Especially the pistachio ice cream was highly praised; we couldn't understand why he was bragging., dataset/taste/sevinc_pastanesi_betul_uzunoglu.png, 2, taste
Sevinc Pastanesi, Cenk Basbolat, Menu was like that. Average business., dataset/menu/sevinc_pastanesi_cenk_basbolat.png, 5, menu
Sevinc Pastanesi, Ian Hooker, Prices too high Turkish coffee 42.5TL Salty cookies weak., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sevinc_pastanesi_ian_hooker.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Ali Cebeci, Spacious; clean and comfortable place. Employees concerned. We didn't wait long for the order. It was one of the best lahmacun I've ever eaten. Prices are affordable., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/hasan_usta_ali_cebeci.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Burak Gelen, It is a place that can be preferred for taste; but the appetizer variety is very weak. The toilets smelled., dataset/menu/hasan_usta_burak_gelen.png, 3, menu
Hasan Usta, Ahmet Alas, The food is very delicious. I congratulate the value and sincerity of the employees in their work., dataset/taste/hasan_usta_ahmet_alas.png, 5, taste
Hasan Usta, Bilal Duzenli, The space is comfortable and spacious. The service is fast; the staff is concerned. There are many types of kebab. We ordered shish shish and Adana; the taste is satisfactory. Prices were like market average., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hasan_usta_bilal_duzenli.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Firat Gurcan, Taste; hygiene; speed;service were all very good. I went for a late dinner; everything was very good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/hasan_usta_firat_gurcan.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Dilan Karaaslan, We came from out of town. Kebab and skewers were great; and the strained yogurt appetizer was delicious; we will definitely come to you next visit., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hasan_usta_dilan_karaaslan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Yildiz Kapidar, The staff is very interested and fast; the environment is very nice; the food and appetizers are very tasty., dataset/taste/hasan_usta_yildiz_kapidar.png, 5, taste
Hasan Usta, Ayse Gokoglu, I liked the kebab and salad; but I can't say the same for their appetizers. It was less in variety; unfortunately; it was unpleasant for those who came. The ambiance was great., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/hasan_usta_ayse_gokoglu.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Hasan Usta, Ferhat Karatay, It's delicious and the prices are reasonable. The appetizers are very filling and satisfying., dataset/menu/hasan_usta_ferhat_karatay.png, 5, menu
Hasan Usta, Metehan Karahan, We were satisfied with the food; but the toilets are very dirty; I am deducting points from this issue., dataset/menu/hasan_usta_metehan_karahan.png, 3, menu
Hasan Usta, Ahmet Demirci, Three Portions of Adana Kebab on one skewer and 3 drinks for 106 TL. My expectation was higher in terms of taste; but I cannot say that I could fully find this expectation. But the side dishes were not bad., dataset/taste/hasan_usta_ahmet_demirci.png, 4, taste

Magro, Selda Can, Everything really appeals to both the eyes and the stomach. They have an incredibly beautiful and varied menu. Prices are reasonable according to the taste; quality and satiety of the menu., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/magro_selca_can.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Magro, Kardelen Acar, Every meal is a source of happiness at Magro. This time we tried chicken with almond sauce and Mac and cheese bolognese; it was delicious. Portions are very filling and very reasonable for the price., dataset/taste/magro_kardelen_acar.png, 5, taste
Magro, Alper Yildirim, Magro is a really nice place in terms of design. I ate chicken broth soup; tomato soup; magro burger and grilled sea bass. Presentation; portion and taste are good. However; it is very expensive.Service sucks., dataset/menu/magro_alper_yildirim.png, 2, menu
Magro, Burak Cam, Unique in Alsancak Kordon.. Good food; especially chicken wrap is awesome., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/magro_burak_cam.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Magro, Sibel Kadirli, It is a classical home breakfast; so it is expensive for home breakfast., dataset/taste/magro_sibel_kadirli.png, 3, taste
Magro, Haluk Suter, Bad breakfast experince for me., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/magro_haluk_suter.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Magro, Fatih Sarac, Everything I ate that in a super menu; was very good. I recommend this place to everyone., dataset/menu/magro_fatih_sarac.png, 5, menu
Magro, Nils Reinke, Great service; great food; everything is great!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/magro_nils_reinke.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Magro, Nevin Gultepe, Nice and beautiful place. The breakfast spread was hearty and good. Prices are normal., dataset/taste/magro_nevin_gultepe.png, 5, taste
Magro, Mustafa Acar, Margarita pizza is pretty good. The atmosphere is also nice. Toilets are very clean., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/magro_mustafa_acar.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Saliha Senyildiz, We came here for the first time; we just tried the doner; it was good; the treats were not bad; the staff was very interested., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_saliha_senyildiz.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Adil Korkmaz, Lahmacun tasted good and was filling. Some of the ingredients used in the salad started to deteriorate., dataset/taste/duveroglu_adil_korkmaz.png, 3, taste
Duveroglu, Aylin Saglam, They've updated the prices and it's as if they have reduced the portions. It is irritating that the edges of the plates are broken., dataset/menu/duveroglu_aylin_saglam.png, 3, menu
Duveroglu, Cihan Kures, Liked., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_cihan_kures.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Murat Cihanoglu, I didn't like Iskender; the meat was not of good quality., dataset/taste/duveroglu_murat_cihanoglu.png, 3, taste
Duveroglu, Cigdem Karakaya, Even though it's not as good as it used to be; it's still my choice. I would be more satisfied if they boiled the stuffed meatballs., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_cigdem_karakaya.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Can Akkaynak, Good in general. Quality for Kızılay and its surroundings. Lahmacun doesn't taste old..., dataset/menu/duveroglu_can_akkaynak.png, 4, menu
Duveroglu, Berkan Serin, I go here for the lahmacun; I haven't tried their other dishes; but the lahmacun is very good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_berkan_serin.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Ali Tavus, I eat it by putting adana kebab in between the lahmacun. Legend is delicious; try it!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_ali_tavus.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Duveroglu, Talip Tarhan, Service is good. Lahmacun was delicious., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/duveroglu_talip_tarhan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere

Rumeli Iskembecisi, Ozgur Akbiyik, Service, respect, taste literally 10/10., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_ozgur_akbiyik.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Kaan Dogu, Definitely a good tripe soup; but I've had much better ones. Very clean place; prices are a bit expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_kaan_dogu.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Mehmet Durmaz, In terms of taste; I can't say it's too good because we drink much better ones. As a business performance; even bread is sold for money alongside soup., dataset/taste/rumeli_iskembecisi_mehmet_durmaz.png, 3, taste
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Buket Aydin, Portion is enough; taste is average; but unfortunately there is no hygiene. We sat in the garden but there was a heavy smell in the environment., dataset/menu/rumeli_iskembecisi_buket_aydin.png, 3, menu
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Efe Arslan, I found the trotter soup I was looking for; it was very nice; thank you. Employees are not friendly., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_efe_arslan.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Abu Ahmet, The trotter soup I drank here is among the top 3 soups I've had in my life. The food of the place is very delicious; the service is impeccable., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_abu_ahmet.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Emre Yildirim, The taste is excellent; the portion size is good; the price is a bit expensive., dataset/taste/rumeli_iskembecisi_emre_yildirim.png, 5, taste
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Adil Kucukaga, Amazing!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_adil_kucukaga.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Rahmi Aydin, The business demands money from everything; no treats!, dataset/menu/rumeli_iskembecisi_rahmi_aydin.png, 4, menu
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Ozcan Oner, Ankara's oldest and most beautiful soup restourant. Soups with very good hygiene can be eaten and drunk with peace of mind. Service is fast. Prices are a little high., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/rumeli_iskembecisi_ozcan_oner.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Rumeli Iskembecisi, Serdar Sezgin, Clean and decent place. I think it would be better if the soup was hot and fresh if there were bread facilities that came with it., dataset/taste/rumeli_iskembecisi_serdar_sezgin.png, 4, taste

Antakya Mutfagi, Ali Erdogan, Thank you very much for bringing the flavors of Antakya here., dataset/taste/antakya_mutfagi_ali_erdogan.png, 5, taste

Mevlana Lokantasi, Hasan Eryigit, There were burnt livers on the liver skewers; and there were uncooked parts in the chops. Good overall taste. Tripe soup is delicious., dataset/taste/mevlana_lokantasi_hasan_eryigit.png, 3, taste

Prices are a little expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mevlana_lokantasi_ozgur_gulmez.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere

Mevlana Lokantasi, Janna Asueva, Good place. Meals were good. Service is also good. There is parking in front for cars., dataset/taste/mevlana_lokantasi_janna_asueva.png, 4, taste

Asucan Restaurant, Turgut Esen, The irresistible taste of chicken; sauce and spice that has been increasing for years., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/asucan_restaurant_turgut_esen.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Asucan Restaurant, Ayhan Burkut, Chicken pan and salad were okay; but not as exaggerated as other reviews., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/asucan_restaurant_ayhan_burkut.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Asucan Restaurant, Rana Akder, Definitely the chicken and the side salads are also very tasty. Prices are cheap compared to this kind of touristic place. The place was a little crowded., dataset/taste/asucan_restaurant_rana_akder.png, 4, taste
Asucan Restaurant, Kjiong Son, Place was not clear., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/asucan_restaurant_kjiong_son.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Asucan Restaurant, Volkan Kahraman, Sandwich's souce was pretty tasty., dataset/menu/asucan_restaurant_volkan_kahraman.png, 4, menu
Asucan Restaurant, Melisa Genc, Super delicious chicken; best in town., dataset/taste/asucan_restaurant_melisa_genc.png, 5, taste
Asucan Restaurant, Berk Celikyurek, The pos device cannot be used; so they only accept cash payments. I think this creates a problem in terms of hygiene., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/asucan_restaurant_berk_celikyurek.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Fatih Buzgan, We ordered stuffed mumbar; artichokes; liked and tamarind sherbet. All of them were good in taste; quality of materials and presentation., dataset/menu/ciya_sofrasi_fatih_buzgan.png, 5, menu
Ciya Sofrasi, Onur Sener, It is one of the must-visit places with its menu that changes every day and includes original local delicacies from all over Turkey. The poppy and pistachio kebabs are a must try., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/ciya_sofrasi_onur_sener.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Sumeyye Aydogan, We really liked our orders. There were dishes on the menu that I have never tried in my life; nice variety., dataset/taste/ciya_sofrasi_sumeyye_aydogan.png, 5, taste
Ciya Sofrasi, Dilek Payanda, Waiters were not very good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/ciya_sofrasi_dilek_payanda.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Nihat Karabiber, Famous place; fast service; caring staff; the taste of the sherbet we tried for the first time was legendary., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/ciya_sofrasi_nihat_karabiber.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Deniz Miray, Our choice was Antep style lahmacun; since I ate it last time; I found it very dry inside; unfortunately the taste of garlic was barely felt. The cleanliness of the place was good., dataset/taste/ciya_sofrasi_deniz_miray.png, 3, taste
Ciya Sofrasi, Efe Efeoglu, The variety is plentiful. Pretty clean and decent. They make very good dishes from the southeast of our country., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/ciya_sofrasi_efe_efeoglu.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Mirhan Ozdemir, Today we had the opportunity to try the stuffed meatballs and lahmacun. We could not taste the meat at all because the cumin in the stuffen meatballs was too much. Lahmacun is good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/ciya_ozdemir_mirhan_ozdemir.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Ciya Sofrasi, Buse Bilgetekin, The waiters are generally very sullen and unhappy. Service is very slow. Nothing extra comes to the table. Even the starter appetizer; which is available in many kebab shops; does not come. Lahmacun was very dry and tasteless., dataset/menu/ciya_sofrasi_buse_bilgetekin.png, 2, menu
Ciya Sofrasi, Mehmet Tilam, Food was good overall. The toilets are so dirty; we are disgusted., dataset/taste/ciya_sofrasi_mehmet_tilam.png, 3, taste
Ciya Sofrasi, Ela Sera, Everything was excellent. Thank you!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/ciya_sofrasi_ela_sera.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Mesut Demirbilek, A perfect view; a friendly and sincere service and great tastes...what more could you ask for?, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_mesut_demirbilek.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Mine Aytekin, The view is great. This may be its only good feature. Apart from that; they have extremely rude employees., dataset/menu/koco_restaurant_mine_aytekin.png, 1, menu
Koco Restaurant, Barkin Kizilkaya, The food is good. The calamari and seafood are delicious. Nice atmosphere opposite the sea. It would have been better if there was some music playing in the venue., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_barkin_kizilkaya.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Muslum Bahceci, Yummy; delicious and wonderful.. The view is as beautiful as the food., dataset/taste/koco_restaurant_muslum_bahceci.png, 5, taste
Koco Restaurant, Cagil Harmandar, We had dinner in a very stylish place with a beautiful view by the sea. The flavors were perfect., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_cagil_harmandar.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Serhat Bayhan, A decent place where you can dine under the trees; accompanied by the moonlight.

4, indoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Muslum Bahceci, Yummy; delicious and wonderful.. The view is as beautiful as the food., dataset/taste/koco_restaurant_muslum_bahceci.png, 5, taste

Koco Restaurant, Serhat Bayhan, A decent place where you can dine under the trees; accompanied by the moonlight. Employees are friendly., dataset/menu/koco_restaurant_serhat_bayhan.png, 4, menu
Koco Restaurant, Arman Senci, Be sure to ask for all prices in advance. You'd definitely get charged triple the price and these guys will try to scam you in all possible ways. Including overcharging the market price; charging you for double the weight of the fish & serving you a half the fillet and all the bones to charge you for all that., dataset/taste/koco_restaurant_arman_senci.png, 1, taste
Koco Restaurant, Osman Kuzgun, The summer part of the place is stylish and pleasant; the view is wonderful. The food and appetizers are delicious. Prices were a little expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_osman_kuzgun.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Nihat Karabiber, Generally good service thank you!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_nihat_karabiber.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Koco Restaurant, Mehmet Kaya, Appetizers are great; the view is great; the place is beautiful; the fish is very fresh and delicious., dataset/taste/koco_restaurant_mehmet_kaya.png, 5, taste
Koco Restaurant, Gungor Koksal, The theme of the place is usually white. This can actually bother the human eye on sunny days; so I think the wrong color was chosen. Fish flavors were average., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/koco_restaurant_gungor_koksal.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Onder Yaman, Food came late; pasta was cold. The waiters couldn't take care of us from taking care of the takeaway., dataset/menu/tavuk_dunyasi_onder_yaman.png, 2, menu
Tavuk Dunyasi, Furkan Yildirim, The ingredients used in the salad were rotten; I didn't like it at all., dataset/taste/tavuk_dunyasi_furkan_yildirim.png, 1, taste
Tavuk Dunyasi, Saygi Kanal, Great chicken; thanks!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_saygi_kanal.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Harun Koybasi, The taste is fine; but when you wait for the waiter for 15 minutes to order and wait for the food for 15 minutes after placing the order; the taste is meaningless. Waiters were very indifferent., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_harun_koybasi.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Yusuf Sezer, Recommend., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_yusuf_sezer.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Ozge Sisar, It had nothing to do with the chicken world flavor I knew., dataset/taste/tavuk_dunyasi_ozge_sisar.png, 3, taste
Tavuk Dunyasi, Cihangir Koyuncu, Very tasty; I definitely recommend. The reason I gave 4 stars is because the prices are expensive., dataset/taste/tavuk_dunyasi_cihangir_koyuncu.png, 4, taste
Tavuk Dunyasi, Erdal Taylan, We ordered cafe de paris; it was delicious; and the price was 35tl., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_erdal_taylan.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Yasemin Beril, It is very crowded and arrives incredibly late. If you are very hungry; it is better to eat somewhere else., dataset/menu/tavuk_dunyasi_yasemin_beril.png, 3, menu
Tavuk Dunyasi, Baki Sarici, Salad was not very fresh., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_baki_sarici.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Tavuk Dunyasi, Lorian Elder, It was a bit crowded; but it's okay; the flavors were good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/tavuk_dunyasi_lorian_elder.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Burcak Kurt, Overall everything was delicious; however; we didn't like the eggplant salad; it was too sour and didn't taste like eggplant at all., dataset/taste/kumsal_lokantasi_burcak_kurt.png, 4, taste
Kumsal Lokantasi, Erkan Baysoy, Raki and fish was good thank you it was super., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_erkan_baysoy.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Taner Diyaz, We went on a Friday and all the tables were full at first. Service; waiters; the ambiance is very nice. The menu was a little expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_taner_diyaz.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Sitki Evrenkaya, Excellent service., dataset/menu/kumsal_lokantasi_sitki_evrenkaya.png, 5, menu
Kumsal Lokantasi, Osman Gunalp, I recommend the liver and Cyprus salad; the appetizers are delicious; the price is good according to the place and the service provided., dataset/taste/kumsal_lokantasi_osman_gunalp.png, 5, taste
Kumsal Lokantasi, Charles Laria, We had a pleasant time. The ambiance was nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_charles_laria.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Bekir Boz, The smell of the wet wipes was very nice. It's a clean place., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_bekir_boz.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Mahmut Kaplan, We ate nice fishes; thank you., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_mahmut_kaplan.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Ceren Yaman, Elite; delicious; central; what more? The most preferred dishes we experienced are sole fish skewers; fried anchovies and shrimp-calamari. They also bring fresh lavash if you want. The sole fish was amazing. Food is also a little pricey., dataset/taste/kumsal_lokantasi_ceren_yaman.png, 5, taste
Kumsal Lokantasi, Sinem Sahin, Thanks for the nice service., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kumsal_lokantasi_sinem_sahin.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kumsal Lokantasi, Bora Gungoren, Nice salad; it was delicious., dataset/taste/kumsal_lokantasi_bora_gungoren.png, 5, taste
Salih Usta, Ilker Ekinci, We randomly decided to stop by and have an ice cream; but we tasted the worst ice cream we've ever had in our lives here. I don't know if it was one of the flavors they used; but the products seemed to be out of date., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/salih_usta_ilker_ekinci.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Salih Usta, Hasan Erdem, Have you ever seen a rainbow in these colors?! The 5-year-old boy would draw the umbrella more beautifully; which was said to be made of sugar dough. The cake doesn't even stand up straight. A birthday cake would only be so sloppy., dataset/taste/salih_usta_hasan_erdem.png, 1, taste
Salih Usta, Mehmet Gemici, The pastry is very nice . It is more affordable compared to other places. I highly recommend other products., dataset/taste/salih_usta_mehmet_gemici.png, 5, taste
Salih Usta, Emre Safak, It is clean and hygiene rules have been followed. The products are daily and fresh.  It is very rich in diversity. Every product you are looking for is available. You can shop without thinking at all., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salih_usta_emre_safak.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Salih Usta, Yilmaz Yasar, Don't order anything at home; they're sending a stale dessert., dataset/taste/salih_usta_yilmaz_yasar.png, 2, taste
Salih Usta, Yeliz Kiziltoprak, I didn't like the atmosphere or the decor either. The lower floor is in front of the highway. Trucks are passing by; you're eating pies. It's not nice and it's expensive. Oh; and there are a lot of beggars., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salih_usta_yeliz_kiziltoprak.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Salih Usta, Busra Subasi, My and my 3.5-year-old daughter's favorite place is in Samsun; we love the products of this place the most., dataset/taste/salih_usta_busra_subasi.png, 5, taste
Salih Usta, Fikret Aslan, They have very high quality cakes; I strongly recommend. Their baklava alone is not that good. Cookies are expensive; but they're fine., dataset/taste/salih_usta_fikret_aslan.png, 3, taste
Salih Usta, Fatih Ege, They have various and delicious products. Especially the age cakes are very successful. The materials they use in the products are of high quality; the prices are reasonable according to the quality., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salih_usta_fatih_ege.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Salih Usta, Furkan Yuksel, You won't regret that the products taste very good; but I've never seen such a bad staff before; definitely don't sit down and drink tea and coffee; take the product and leave; that's the most logical thing., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/salih_usta_furkan_yuksel.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Salih Usta, Aysel Hasir, it is a very nice place for high quality and special tastes; the employees and the owner are very interested and polite; we are going with love., dataset/taste/salih_usta_aysel_hasir.png, 4, taste
Red Dragon, Teoman Sezer, Chinese salad and spring rolls were okay. I didn't like the veggie noodles very much. The plum sauce of the peking duck was delicious but the presentation was poor., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_teoman_sezer.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Baran Seyyar, A place with a nice ambiance and delicious sushi. It may be called expensive; but unfortunately; the taste is not affordable., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_baran_seyyar.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Enes Sert, The ambiance of the place is nice but the food is not tasty. I don't think I will come again., dataset/menu/red_dragon_enes_sert.png, 2, menu
Red Dragon, Ediz Aksoy, When you come to the front of the place; its magnificent exterior design really draws attention and I think it was done very well and I personally liked it very much. The atmosphere is truly magnificent. We tried Chinese food; especially ramen was delicious., dataset/taste/red_dragon_ediz_aksoy.png, 5, taste
Red Dragon, Bilge Cakir, The atmosphere is nice and the food is delicious. We tried noodles, spring rolls; hot and sour soup and an apple dessert., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_bilge_cakir.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Ender Gulsen, Food was a bit salty due to soy sauce. Prices are in line with the market., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_ender_gulsen.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Muhsine Ozer, The plate in the photo was around 340 TL. Flavors may be a bit difficult for those who will try for the first time., dataset/taste/red_dragon_muhsine_ozer.png, 3, taste
Red Dragon, Mustafa Kadim, I tried peking duck with orange and soy sauce. It had a somewhat offensive odor. Good in terms of taste., dataset/menu/red_dragon_mustafa_kadim.png, 4, menu
Red Dragon, Elfin Siner, It has cheaper price compared to other chinese restaurants. But the flavors were not that good. What was particularly interesting to me was that the drinks were very expensive., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_elfin_siner.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Tuvanna Kuscu, The outside and inside of the restaurant is very well decorated. The ambiance is really nice. We ate sushi; chicken with mushrooms and steamed ravioli. I really liked the sushi and chicken; but I found the ravioli a bit bland., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_tuvanna_kuscu.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Tugce Atalay, We ate 3 Bentos and 3 Mixed Noodles. We liked everything we ate; it was very tasty. The service was fast; but it was a bit expensive for your information., dataset/taste/red_dragon_tugce_atalay.png, 5, taste

Dragon, Tuvanna Kuscu, The outside and inside of the restaurant is very well decorated. The ambiance is really nice. We ate sushi; chicken with mushrooms and steamed ravioli. I really liked the sushi and chicken; but I found the ravioli a bit bland., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/red_dragon_tuvanna_kuscu.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Red Dragon, Tugce Atalay, We ate 3 Bentos and 3 Mixed Noodles. We liked everything we ate; it was very tasty. The service was fast; but it was a bit expensive for your information., dataset/taste/red_dragon_tugce_atalay.png, 5, taste
Mado, Tugay Kutlu, One of the places in Samsun with the most beautiful view and menu. A place where you can enjoy your dessert and coffee to the full while enjoying the sea view in front., dataset/menu/mado_tugay_kutlu.png, 4, menu
Mado, Zafer Caner, First of all; the service is slow and very late; and there are no crowds. I ordered a bulk profiterole. The portion also had 4 balls the size of nuts; and the chocolate was also tasteless., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mado_zafer_caner.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Mado, Sumeyye Gulten, Atakum Mado... What a need for another word... The taste;  quality of the products are ala. It is very nice that the service staff is kind; solution-oriented. Especially the sensitivity of the company official; it is very nice to be relevant., dataset/taste/mado_sumeyye_gulten.png, 5, taste
Mado, Melike Gulsen, There is no need to tell Mado at length; it is a clean and beautiful place.  But there is no standard; kadayif burma with pistachios used to be so unique that I would like to eat it everyday. But now sometimes it was burnt; sometimes dry; sometimes uncooked., dataset/taste/mado_melike_gulsen.png, 3, taste
Mado, Ali Berk Kustul, Well; it was very nice; the service was very fast and the prices are reasonable; I recommend delicious food., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mado_ali_berk_kustul.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Mado, Deniz Ozbekturk, I wanted a four-cheese ravioli. It's just that the sauce is nice. Unfortunately; it failed. All of the portions have adapted to the economy; they have shrunk., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mado_deniz_ozbekturk.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Mado, Cetin Atali, My guest and I went for dessert;  we waited 10 minutes to get a menu; we placed orders; and we waited another 20 minutes. Of course; one person couldn't make it to the dozens of tables upstairs to work., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mado_cetin_atali.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Mado, Asuman Mutevellioglu, It may be the most friendly service I have ever encountered in my life.  All the employees were very sweet; caring people. the drinks and food were very tasty and fresh. I will definitely come again., dataset/taste/mado_asuman_mutevellioglu.png, 5, taste
Mado, Engin Kapan, Something strange came out of the ice cream; the teas are stale and boiled; and you have to say an order two or three times; I definitely don't recommend it; it's a pity for your money., dataset/menu/mado_engin_kapan.png, 2, menu
Mado, Muhammet Ay, The address of quality. The service should be a little faster., dataset/taste/mado_muhammet_ay.png, 4, taste
Mado, Gokhan Basturk, Unfortunately; the sorbet desserts are not satisfactory. The air conditioners are not working. It's a humid environment. I hope they fix it., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mado_gokhan_basturk.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Miley Sinus, Love this restaurant; thai style and good taste. Clean and good service.. Recommended !, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_miley_sinus.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Merve Sever, I loved the ambiance; welcome and service. We ate pineapple; spicy shrimp; chicken noodles; and chicken pie. A little pricey but nice place., dataset/taste/classic_thai_merve_sever.png, 3, taste
Classic Thai, Abdullah Eser, You can taste different flavors on the menus. It's a bit of an expensive place. The waiters are nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_abdullah_eser.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Dogan Akyel, Amazing flavors!, dataset/menu/classic_thai_dogan_akyel.png, 5, menu
Classic Thai, Kadir Sandal, Ambiance were pretty good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_kadir_sandal.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Hamad Almuftad, I like thailand foods but not like here ones., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_hamad_almuftad.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Ebru Sakar, The food is very good; the employees are very good and smiling. Prices are very reasonable compared to Asian cuisines. I will come here often., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_ebru_sakar.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Maria Taison, We’ve had a great dinner at this restaurant. The food was delicious; well prepared and nicely seasoned. I did not know much about Thai cuisine; but I enjoyed the meal very much. Plus the atmosphere of the place is relaxing; staff nice and friendly and prices pretty moderate. Perfect spot to eat out with friends in the center of Istanbul. Would love to come back again!, dataset/taste/classic_thai_maria_taison.png, 4, taste
Classic Thai, Alev Ozturk, Although far easts foods suits my taste; Tom Yum soup was very aromatic and different; I didn't like it., dataset/menu/classic_thai_alev_ozturk.png, 5, menu
Classic Thai, Theodore Rano, The waiters took care of me. That's why I left the restaurant before I could order., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/classic_thai_theodore_rano.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Classic Thai, Degen Hill, Egg dish was super salty. Beef with veggies was really good. A bit on the pricier side compared with local Turkish food; but when your Thai GF wants a taste of home; hard to argue over price., dataset/taste/classic_thai_degen_hill.png, 4, taste
Inegol Restaurant, Muhammet Uygun, The staff is very nice. The food is quite delicious., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_muhammet_uygun.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Mehmet Cakir, The environment is nice, the food is delicious, the employees are polite. We ate meatballs in İnegöl. the manti were great., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_mehmet_cakir.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Burak Yilmaz, It's an expensive restaurant., dataset/menu/inegol_restaurant_burak_yilmaz.png, 1, menu
Inegol Restaurant, Aysenur Celik, I especially recommend wedding soup; stuffed meatballs; manti and Inegöl meatballs., dataset/taste/inegol_restaurant_aysenur_celik.png, 4, taste
Inegol Restaurant, Murat Gul, Local dishes and soups are nice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_murat_gul.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Erkan Yilmaz, I did not recommend. Bad service., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_erkan_yilmaz.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Selim Burusuk, The place is beautiful; the food sucks. Also expensive., dataset/menu/inegol_restaurant_selim_burusuk.png, 4, menu
Inegol Restaurant, Selman Genc, We came because the comments were good; we did not regret it. I recommend the beef tenderloin. Home baklava is also very tasty; prices are reasonable., dataset/taste/inegol_restaurant_selman_genc.png, 5, taste
Inegol Restaurant, Huseyin Demirel, Delicious food; but their toilets are filthy. That's why I'm deducting points., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_huseyin_demirel.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Cenk Ozmercan, Famous and delicious meatballs., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/inegol_restaurant_cenk_ozmercan.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Inegol Restaurant, Osman Korkmaz, The food is delicious; but we waited 1 hour after ordering and we were extremely hungry., dataset/taste/inegol_restaurant_osman_korkmaz.png, 1, taste
Karakoy Lokantasi, Baris Efe, I ate Hünkar Begendi and cherry pudding. Both were legends. The meat of Hünkar Begendi was tender., dataset/menu/karakoy_lokantasi_baris_efe.png, 5, menu
Karakoy Lokantasi, Soykan Ozdemir, It has been wonderfully designed in its new location in Karaköy. It's gorgeous inside. Soundproofing I guess. The waiters are very interested and approaching with a smile. The appetizers and great service were very successful. Thanks., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/karakoy_lokantasi_soykan_ozdemir.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Karakoy Lokantasi, Alper Uner, A classy place in Karaköy with its white cloth and good service. Liver lovers should definitely try the liver pan., dataset/taste/karakoy_lokantasi_alper_uner.png, 5, taste
Karakoy Lokantasi, Yavuz Parla, The location is nice; the menus are varied; the appetizers are delicious; the prices are a little high., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/karakoy_lokantasi_yavuz_parla.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Karakoy Lokantasi, Oncu Guyer, Excellent appetizers; great atmosphere; acceptable prices., dataset/menu/karakoy_lokantasi_oncu_guyer.png, 5, menu
Karakoy Lokantasi, Ece Oztunc, The place was too noisy. We didn't really enjoy the food in this mess., dataset/taste/karakoy_lokantasi_ece_oztunc.png, 3, taste
Karakoy Lokantasi, Pelin Kuzey, Some of the seafood starters are successful. Appetizers are small in portion size for one person. Salads do not meet expectations., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/karakoy_lokantasi_pelin_kuzey.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Karakoy Lokantasi, Mevlut Sahin, Awesome place!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/karakoy_lokantasi_mevlut_sahin.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Karakoy Lokantasi, Burak Tuzel, I can't say anything negative about the place, the ambiance; the staff; the richness of the food; the appetizers; the taste and the presentation; it's just perfect.. But I'm giving 3 points because it's a very expensive place., dataset/taste/karakoy_lokantasi_burak_tuzel.png, 3, taste

Karakoy Lokantasi, Filiz Goksever, Yummy yummy! Delicious!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/karakoy_lokantasi_filiz_goksever.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Mahmut Demir, The treats and the food were really delicious; each of them was not one of those places that would cause you to come to the place and leave unhappy., dataset/taste/mersinli_cigerci_apo_mahmut_demir.png, 5, taste
Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Emre Abalak, We came up with the suggestion; everything was very nice.Especially Koksal; who was in the safe; was so interested. Thank you so much for everything., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/mersinli_cigerci_apo_emre_abalak.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Hayrullah Unal, Although it is not as much as an urfa; it is the only place that can eat liver under samsun conditions. Appetizers can be improved. Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Gokhan Guzel, Its breakfast is really very good. I would like to especially point out that you do not need to go to Cakalli for Menemen; you can eat the most delicious here. I really like the fried egg too., dataset/taste/mersinli_cigerci_apo_gokhan_guzel.png, 5, taste
Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Mutlu Inac, They've reduced the menus so much that you can't get enough. The service was over., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mersinli_cigerci_apo_mutlu_inac.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere

Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Hulya Bezci, The staff is extremely interested; the taste is already a very good place. It is recommended., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mersinli_cigerci_apo_hulya_bezci.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Mersinli Cigerci Apo, Levent Sun, The food wasn't bad; we got tired of constantly asking for lavash bread; the liver; until the bread came to the table it became like ice., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/mersinli_cigerci_apo_levent_sun.png, 2, indoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Serdar Soylu, It is a great place for Samsun. The taste; the treats; the semolina dessert with ice cream that comes after the meal; the variety of the menu; the attention and politeness of the waiters are very good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/baskent_aspava_serdar_soylu.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Ibrahim Genc, We went to Iftar; especially they praised the appetizers and treats very much; but as can be seen from the photo; it's not good at all. It was an incredible crowd., dataset/taste/baskent_aspava_ibrahim_genc.png, 3, taste
Baskent Aspava, Emine Cinar, It's delicious; fast and has friendly staff. Although the price seems a little expensive; it meets this with unlimited tea; dessert service and appetizers., dataset/menu/baskent_aspava_emine_cinar.png, 4, menu
Baskent Aspava, Murat Caliskan, The place is nice; the employees are good. The food is delicious but the human pilfering for extra charge caused me to give it 1 point., dataset/menu/baskent_aspava_murat_caliskan.png, 1, menu
Baskent Aspava, Burak Ak, Congratulations; everything was very nice and attentive. The treats were too much for the number of people. Cacik is given in aspava in Ankara; this can also be included in the treats; I can say this in addition., dataset/taste/baskent_aspava_burak_ak.png, 4, taste
Baskent Aspava, Melike Erdem, The prices were in the 120-140 range. I didn't like Lahmacun. The appetizers were nice., dataset/taste/baskent_aspava_melike_erdem.png, 2, taste
Baskent Aspava, Metehan Naz, Every time I go; the prices change; I don't like it. But even for the treats; you can go; which comes as many appetizers; tea; etc. as you want., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/baskent_aspava_metehan_naz.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Taner Gurel, We went for dinner. after 10 minutes; they said do you want meatball; we bought 1 piece; we asked for an account of 32TL; then they reflected it to the account; they put water in the glasses unannounced; they wrote 20TL to the 1.5 liter water on the table. They're not supposed to do it this way., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/baskent_aspava_taner_gurel.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Gun Oksay, The sauces and uncooked meats of the dishes give the impression of a meal prepared in the mall and not in a kebab restaurant., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/baskent_aspava_gun_oksay.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Bulent Ozengin, Very; very expensive extravagant prices. One lahmacun is 85 TL. They charge 25 TL for a glass of buttermilk. All the intertwined tables are almost adjacent., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/baskent_aspava_bulent_ozengin.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Baskent Aspava, Cagla Arslan, I ate closed doner pita pita were very tasty. Iskender was beautiful. There is a playground for children. Great on treats., dataset/taste/baskent_aspava_cagla_arslan.png, 5, taste
Sini Mugla, Amine Caliskan, Prices are reasonable; foods were delicious., dataset/menu/sini_mugla_amine_caliskan.png, 4, menu
Sini Mugla, Ipek Cicek, The place was full of flies and one of them fell into my food. When I asked for my meal to be changed,; they refused., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_ipek_cicek.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Sini Mugla, Yunus Mutlu, The atmosphere was spacious and the waiters were nice. The meals were very delicious... the prices were reasonable; but the portions were small., dataset/taste/sini_mugla_yunus_mutlu.png, 4, taste
Sini Mugla, Sevgi Kizilirmak, The food is super delicious; I especially recommend the fig dessert. Service personnel interest and hygiene were also high., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_sevgi_kizilirmak.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sini Mugla, Yusuf Serin, Dirty plates; Waiters was surly., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_yusuf_serin.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Sini Mugla, Gulden Ulualp, The meals were delicious. Service is fast; transportation is easy; staff is friendly. Prices are quite reasonable., dataset/taste/sini_mugla_gulden_ulualp.png, 5, taste
Sini Mugla, Sibel Salis, The waiters are scruffy so we didn't feel comfortable eating. The hygiene of the place was also bad., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_sibel_salis.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Sini Mugla, Soner Tufekci, Great ambiance!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_soner_tufekci.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Sini Mugla, Kadir Hurok, Salad was great; appetizers were good. The degree of cooking of the meat was good. Also the toilets were very clean., dataset/taste/sini_mugla_kadir_hurok.png, 4, taste
Sini Mugla, Sukru Ardic, Portions were small but expensive., dataset/menu/sini_mugla_sukru_ardic.png, 3, menu
Sini Mugla, Mehmet Soybilge, The satisfying menu of local dishes; the taste of the food and the interest of the employees are very good. The advantage is that it is on the road and has its own parking lot., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/sini_mugla_mehmet_soybilge.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Emrah Sozen, Everything was excellent; especially sea foods!, dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_emrah_sozen.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Can Ocakli, Bosphorus Salad; Shrimp Cizlama were really successful. Orders came to my table quickly., dataset/taste/fikret_balik_restaurant_can_ocakli.png, 5, taste
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Tarik Esdik, I am a regular at this place; and I love it as a family The food is fantastic; the fish are great!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_tarik_esdik.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Ozge Askan, Food was a little expensive but it is ok., dataset/menu/fikret_balik_restaurant_ozge_askan.png, 3, menu
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Tarik Miroglu, Clean place; the service is good; Prices are not very cheap. generally the Arabs are leaving; locals are also present. Service is fast., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_tarik_miroglu.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Hilal Ozden, Portions were quite adequate. Along with your meal comes multiple and delicious appetizers. Seasonal salad was also delicious; vegetables were fresh., dataset/taste/fikret_balik_restaurant_hilal_ozden.png, 4, taste
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Samet Cevik, A restaurant where you can eat amazing seafood in a great atmosphere in Bursa. Its taste will really surprise you. I would like to remind you that there is no Alcohol in the restaurant. Bon appetit now!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_samet_cevik.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Mustafa Karaarslan, Expensive place., dataset/menu/fikret_balik_restaurant_mustafa_karaarslan.png, 1, menu
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Munevver Demir, We ordered a soup and a portion of haddock. The bread was great; the eggplant paste was also very good. The soup was delicious; the haddock was delicious., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_munevver_demir.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Sefa Dalan, The environment is decent; the service is fast and clean. The interior is spacious; the waiters are knowledgeable and respectful., dataset/taste/fikret_balik_restaurant_sefa_dalan.png, 5, taste
Fikret Balik Restaurant, Volkan Kamadan, The assortment is exceptionally good. Fish and accompanying appetizers are very diverse and sufficient. Everything was fresh., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/fikret_balik_restaurant_volkan_kamadan.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kocak Baklava, Huseyin Ozcalkap, The place was nice; but be aware of an expensive place., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kocak_baklava_huseyin_ozcalkap.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Kocak Baklava, Sukru Arici, The flavors are still fabulous; Prices may change according to the conditions of the day. But the taste is always great., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kocak_baklava_sukru_arici.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Kocak Baklava, Sabahat Yilmaz, Their desserts were really good and tasty but the prices were high., dataset/taste/kocak_baklava_sabahat_yilmaz.png, 4, taste
Kocak Baklava, Turgay Ogutlu, We ate an excellent baklava. But the price wasn't perfect., dataset/menu/kocak_baklava_turgat_ogutlu.png, 5, menu

It is the number ten place for me with its understanding of both quality and service. When I come to Gaziantep again; I want to stop by here again and eat this baklava again., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kocak_baklava_cem_baba.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere

Kocak Baklava, Sadrettin Guner, The staff; the dessert; the place; the ambiance; everything is very nice. It was the best baklava I have ever eaten in my life!, dataset/taste/kocak_baklava_sadrettin_guner.png, 5, taste

J Burber, Ilke Cakmakoglu, Burgers and fries were delicious. Burger meat came well cooked; I suggest you eat it medium cooked. The sauces are quite different and nice; you should definitely try it., dataset/taste/j_burger_ilke_cakmakoglu.png, 4, taste
J Burber, Mete Yazgic, Too expensive; I can cook better. Also; ambiance of the restaurant is old., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/j_burger_mete_yazgic.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Ferhat Bascil, Prices are reasonable; chickens are delicious; but what is on the menu is not real. They do not serve the same food as the menu., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/popeyes_ferhat_bascil.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Melisa Sen, My order was missing sauce; missing desert; missing onion rings; fries were cold and stale; fried legs were stale. What a disgrace!, dataset/taste/popeyes_melisa_sen.png, 1, taste
Popeyes, Mirac Kilic, They got my order wrong and got into an argument with me. You are disgusting! Terrible service; mismanagement., dataset/menu/popeyes_mirac_kilic.png, 1, menu
Popeyes, Nail Beyazit, Food should have been better cooked I think overall not bad., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/popeyes_nail_beyazit.png, 4, outdoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Murat Arslan, Everything is delicious; there is a lot and at a good price. Service was nice., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/popeyes_murat_arslan.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Kenan Yildirim, The taste is not bad in general; but you can eat better ones in other restaurants., dataset/taste/popeyes_kenan_yildirim.png, 4, taste
Popeyes, Majid Khoddami, No management; food is cold and bad quality; no ice in coke. Not happy at all. I recommend either change the airport manager or close that branch. Definitely bad service., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/popeyes_majid_khoddami.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Josiah Wadsack, Classical chicken; not awesome taste but it is ok., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/popeyes_josiah_wadsack.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Popeyes, Emrah Acar, The manners of the employees were bad; They didn't even care about me. Bread was stale., dataset/menu/popeyes_emrah_acar.png, 3, menu
Popeyes, Orhan Kadirli, I couldn't finish my meal .Bad smell and bad taste. It seems that the chicken is spoiled. I don't know what to say; but you should not eat in this place. I feel bad because I decided to eat from them., dataset/taste/popeyes_orhan_kadirli.png, 2, taste
Popeyes, Zehra Ozturk, Delicious and reasonably priced!, dataset/taste/popeyes_zehra_ozturk.png, 5, taste
Say Cheese, Ayhan Karakus, The waiters are polite and very interested. The place consists of two concepts; you can eat standing or sitting. The flavors were perfect., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/say_cheese_ayhan_karakus.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Say Cheese, Ilgaz Ilgin, Pasta was fresh. There is always a long queue in front of the place. I ate fettuccine Alfredo; The sauce and flavor were good., dataset/menu/say_cheese_ilgaz_ilgin.png, 5, menu
Say Cheese, Nur Yoruk, It was served quickly even though it was crowded. It is not a great taste; but it can be preferred for a quick snack., dataset/taste/say_cheese_nur_yoruk.png, 4, taste
Say Cheese, Murat Toprak, Great taste., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/say_cheese_murat_toprak.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Say Cheese, Omer Avci, There are many queues. There is a lack of coordination in the place. Even though you ask for service; they take the bill as soon as the food arrives. Not everyone can eat sitting down; We ate standing., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/say_cheese_omer_avci.png, 1, outdoor_atmosphere
Say Cheese, Saniye Atga, A delicious masterpiece comes out when it is made in a Parmesan wheel; made with fresh pasta dough by hand; and with its beautiful sauces. The price is also quite reasonable., dataset/taste/say_cheese_saniye_atga.png, 4, taste
Say Cheese, Su Mericci, Personally; it's very nice Pasta is made; I tried most of the sauces; they were all very good., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/say_cheese_su_mericci.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Say Cheese, Batuhan Demirci, It's a very sweet place. Thanks to social media; I learned from there and came. Pasta wasn't bad. In terms of taste; I think it is no different from normal pasta with sauce. The employees are very kind. Order speed is very good. Also; prices are affordable., dataset/taste/say_cheese_batuhan_demirci.png, 4, taste
Say Cheese, Doga Keskin, There are two parts that you can eat standing or sitting; I'm sure it will be much more enjoyable if you eat sitting down. It is served pretty fast. Prices are reasonable compared to peers., dataset/menu/say_cheese_doga_keskin.png, 3, menu
Say Cheese, Emre Gudul, Incredibly delicious and fresh; fast service and use of environmentally friendly materials.., dataset/taste/say_cheese_emre_gudul.png, 5, taste
Say Cheese, Kagan Erdogan, Pasta is made there; orders are taken and served. All of them are prepared in one place in 20-25 minutes. The taste is good; the service is good and hygienic; I think it is a taste and culture that should be visited and tasted., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/say_cheese_kagan_erdogan.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Berna Yazici, We went for dessert; but there are also food and breakfast options. It's not a huge venue and it gets pretty busy. We ate moblan; ibiza; strawberry puff pastry desserts. Moblan comes in huge portions. Desserts are very tasty and fresh., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_berna_yazici.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Nermin Yurtoglu, Kukis is a great business that is both a bakery and a patisserie. Their cakes and tea are outstanding., dataset/taste/kukis_suadiye_nermin_yurtoglu.png, 4, taste
Kukis Suadiye, Beyhan Mutlu, Reasonable prices and amazing deserts., dataset/menu/kukis_suadiye_beyhan_mutlu.png, 5, menu
Kukis Suadiye, Sabri Gursoy, The cake was amazing. I recommend it. For those who want to sit and eat there; a big queue is waiting for you., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_sabri_gursoy.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Necla Celik, Their products are delicious and the sizes are nice. It is very difficult to take orders from the waiters because it is crowded. In addition; the prices should have been more affordable., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_necla_celik.png, 3, indoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Serap Aslan, Service is fast. Pistachio prince dessert is excellent!, dataset/indoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_serap_aslan.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Merve Kutukoglu, The portion of toast was small; never satiated. Desserts were good., dataset/taste/kukis_suadiye_merve_kutukoglu.png, 4, taste
Kukis Suadiye, Mustafa Aydemir, Great tastes; the interest of the employees was very good; thank you to them., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_mustafa_aydemir.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Kukis Suadiye, Gozde Sahinyilmaz, If you want to eat cake or dessert; the real taste is here. The place is very stylish in design. Each of the employees is very caring and helpful; but they have difficulty dealing with everyone because it is crowded., dataset/menu/kukis_suadiye_gozde_sahinyilmaz.png, 5, menu
Kukis Suadiye, Ozdogan Kevser, Desserts are good but waiters are very surly; We were not well received., dataset/taste/kukis_suadiye_ozdogan_kevser.png, 3, taste
Kukis Suadiye, Vildan Sarioglu, You should not drink coffee; it tasted very bad. I felt like I was drinking earth. Other than that things are nice., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/kukis_suadiye_vildan_sarioglu.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Barkin Kizilkaya, Great venue great food appetizers. I can be a customer from now on., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/lipa_barkin_kizilkaya.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Selin Yoruk, The meals are very good. Especially plevlevisca; soka and dried meat are very successful., dataset/taste/lipa_selin_yoruk.png, 5, taste
Lipa, Kaim Bros, I did not like the interior atmosphere; seems a little old to me., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/lipa_kaim_bros.png, 2, outdoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Mehrin Kaya, The place is quite intimate and the ambiance is very pleasant. Simplicity prevails rather than exaggeration and ostentatiousness., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/lipa_mehrin_kaya.png, 5, indoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Baris Efe, I recommend you try the dried meat. But their beers were a bit expensive., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/lipa_baris_efe.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Yelda Ay, Expensive place., dataset/menu/lipa_yelda_ay.png, 3, menu
Lipa, Zeynep Barista, All meals were successful; I recommend., dataset/taste/lipa_zeynep_barista.png, 4, taste
Lipa, Sema Yildiz, Lipa is a real old style tavern. There is a warm friendly atmosphere. Dry meat was very good., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/lipa_sema_yildiz.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Murat Sahin, Great and chill place; ambiance was nice too., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/lipa_murat_sahin.png, 3, outdoor_atmosphere
Lipa, Ozgun Onder, The atmosphere of the place is very good; the bulgur pilaf with dried meat was very good; the quality of the dried meat is a little low., dataset/taste/lipa_ozgun_onder.png, 5, taste
Lipa, Mert Gezgin, The variety is less. Rice and dry meat are very good. The ravioli was not good., dataset/menu/lipa_mert_gezgin.png, 4, menu
Minoa, Oznur Akbas, Beautiful; cute; stylish and delicious food. It's a bit sad that it is used more like a restaurant than a book cafe; as it turns into a restaurant at a certain time of the evening; so they took us to a place in the back., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/minoa_oznur_akbas.png, 4, indoor_atmosphere
Minoa, Melis Sezer, A nice place to drink coffee while reading a book. My meat dish arrived cold first. When I reported this to the waiter; they warmed it up and brought it; and then the meat was dry. I did not see the interest that I expected., dataset/taste/minoa_melis_sezer.png, 3, taste
Minoa, Bunyamin Yalcin, A very well designed cafe; The library looks very stylish. The menu is as you can see in the photo., dataset/menu/minoa_bunyamin_yalcin.png, 4, menu
Minoa, Sibel Dursun, Nice and fresh ambiance., dataset/outdoor_atmosphere/minoa_sibel_dursun.png, 5, outdoor_atmosphere
Minoa, Asude Cinkir, Flat white is very tasty and affordable. The interior of the place is very nicely decorated; I was like amazed., dataset/taste/minoa_asude_cinkir.png, 4, taste
Minoa, Ayse Tozal, Interior and location are nice; but not as nice as other restaurant of the same company. We bought a strawberry brownie cake; my friend and I both had a bad stomach., dataset/indoor_atmosphere/minoa_ayse_tozal.png, 1, indoor_atmosphere
